PublicRemarks: This spacious and modern SE corner unit in the historic WOODWARD's building offers a comfortable and luxurious living experience. With 2 bedrooms (+flex) & 2 bathrooms there is plenty of room for relaxation and productivity. Floor to ceiling windows allow for natural light, the stainless steel appliances add a sleek and contemporary touch. Plenty of in-suite storage.   The rooftop amenities, Club W is a highlight, featuring panoramic views, an indoor/outdoor lounging area, library / media room, exercise center &  the hot tub in the shape of a W adds a unique touch to the building.  24-hour concierge, 1 parking & pets / rentals are welcome. Situated in a prime location with easy access to art galleries, boutique shops, and gourmet restaurants, promising a dynamic and exhilarating lifestyle. Open Sun Feb 18 1-3pm (29323265)

PublicRemarks: Find your direction at the COMPASS! this gorgeous two level condo feels like a "townhouse in the sky" and offers the best of Vancouver - a downtown-style, amenity-filled building minutes from the region's best recreation. Thoughtfully designed, the upstairs features a beautiful kitchen with quartz countertops, gas cooktop and a large eat-in island. The bright great room and dining area open onto a very large patio. The lower floor features a primary bedroom with a relaxing spa-like ensuite, an additional full bath, 2nd bedroom and den/office/storage for all your outdoor gear. Includes 1 parking/1 storage. Be part of award winning Seylynn Village only 10 min from Downtown & steps from hiking/biking/parks! Enjoy access to luxury 14,000sf. Denna Club with infinity pool/hot tub/full gym/saunas/party room/yoga room plus a new community rec centre opening nearby in 2024. Priced to sell!  Don't miss this great opportunity. Photos virtually staged. (29259397)

PublicRemarks: MODE presents this 1210sf south facing 2 bedroom+flex+2bath home in River District Vancouver. MODE is one of the tallest concrete highrises in RD. Equipped with premium appliances: gas range, wall-oven & built-in microwave, fully integrated fridge & dishwasher, and quartz countertop and backsplash. Well thought out layout with bedroom separation, energy-efficient in-floor heating in master ensuite, and high efficiency heating and cooling system. MODE is steps from Town Centre retailers and lush green space along with outstanding on site amenities including hot tub, daytime concierge, work hub,theater room,two guest suites, dog wash, large fitness facility, work shop and more. Sales center open Thursday-Monday from ll-4pm. TURN KEY PRICING $50,000 CREDIT! (29151205)

PublicRemarks: Spacious NW Corner unit, 2 Bedroom 2 BATH & DEN in the heart of DOWNTOWN VANCOUVER, with vibrant city views. Large living and dining area with big windows bringing in natural sunlight. Bright and Spacious kitchen leading to a covered sizeable balcony. Walking distance to Yaletown, Robson Street, Pacific Centre, shopping, restaurants and Parks. Minutes to Subway station. Enjoy access to Rosedale Hotel Amenities (indoor pool, hot tub, sauna & gym) with small annual fees. Other amenities including second floor garden, guest parking. One parking and one locker included. Wall paint and carpet replaced in 2019. OPEN HOUSE BY APPOINTMENT ONLY at FEB 17 (Sat) 2-4pm. Pls confirm the appt with me (or through your agent) if you're coming so that I can notify anyone in case of changes since it's tenanted. Tks (29356314)

PublicRemarks: Looking for the  ultimate  Olympic Village lifestyle. Welcome to Kayak!  This spectacular 2-bedroom and large solarium condo has a townhouse feeling and opens right on to a  gorgeous, lushes  green courtyard. German imported kitchen, and luxury faucets throughout. PublicRemarks: Welcome to Navio by Concert Properties. This bright, air-conditioned home has an open concept layout and is located in the heart of Olympic Village. It is a rare 1-bed + Den & Flex room - with the den being large enough to convert into a second bedroom. Being on the north side of the building, you have peek-a-boo water & mountain views with plenty of windows. The modern kitchen is well equipped with elite integrated Bosch appliances, custom cabinetry & Caesarstone counters. This luxury building includes full-time concierge, fitness centre & two rooftop garden terraces. Just steps to the scenic seawall, Skytrain, Science World and everything Main Street & Olympic Village has to offer. This is the one you have been waiting for! 1 parking & 1 storage locker. (29293311)

PublicRemarks: Discover luxury living in the sought-after Hunter building in North Vancouver's rapidly growing Lynn Creek neighborhood. This North facing unit features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an open layout, and a stunning balcony with valley and mountain views, overlooking Lynn Creek and Seylynn Park. Enjoy a variety of amenities like a spa, sauna, exercise room, outdoor BBQ area, private courtyard, gym, social lounge, wellness center and air-conditioning. The new pedestrian bridge provides easy access to Bridgman Park, the Spirit Train and nearby shops. The owner has added adjustable pot lights in the living room for character, and you'll also find an oversized wheelchair-accessible bathroom. The seller's mortgage is eligible for assumption at a fixed interest rate of 4.59% until October 2027. (29146377)

PublicRemarks: JAMESON HOUSE - a contemporary masterpiece by renowned architects Foster + Partners. Located in the heart of the business/financial & entertainment districts and steps to the seawall, shops & restaurants. The open-concept layout features elegantly curved walls, is flooded with natural light, boasts high ceilings and walks-out to a private patio with City, Coal Harbour & Mountain views. Enjoy beautiful, imported travertine flooring that carries out onto  your view terrace, Italian kitchen designed by Dada Cucina featuring Gaggenau and Sub-Zero appliances. Closets by Molteni & C. and a stunning bathroom. 24-hr concierge and auto valet parking system for your convenience. The quality of this home & development does impress. Must be seen to be appreciated! (29330410)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to this spacious 2 Bedroom 2 Bathrooms + Den apartment unit in Coal Harbour. This  intimate apartment complex with simple systems is just steps to the Seawall, Stanley Park, restaurants, grocery, shopping & transit. PublicRemarks: TOWNHOUSE style condo!! 2 bdrms plus a den! When seeking more space & privacy than what is typical apartment has to offer, this two level home is the perfect solution! This unique & well designed home features entries from both the 5th & 6th floors, offering ample space & privacy with a townhome feel. This chic EAST facing 2 bed & den, 2 bath home has 2 entrances & offers open concept living. The main level has a modern kitchen w/high end appliances including a gas range, new fridge, quartz counters, island w/eating bar & large 160 square foot deck w/BBQ gas hookup. Lower level features 2 bedroom & den & 2 baths. Triple glazed windows, 1 parking, storage. Maintenance fee includes concierge, air con, heat, hot water, gas & the world class Denna Club resort facilities. (29308517)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to your new home. Thoughtfully renovated & lovingly maintained two level secure townhouse style living in the heart of Langara. With flex/bed room & three piece bath down, & full size living space up, this home is ideal for those seeking separate living space for working from home, kids, or guests. Rooms large enough to hold your full-size furniture, including a king in MBR with room to spare. Just a few of the special touches that await you in this pristine home include custom kitchen, built ins, pantry, and oak & heated tile flooring. And to top it off, a quiet, sunny South facing balcony with treetop views, & North balcony off MBR. Walking distance to Langara College, YMCA, Canada Line & the new Oakridge, easy access to YVR & rapid bus to UBC. Move right in & enjoy. (29218478)

PublicRemarks: Rarely do renovated New York style lofts become available in the sought-after New Yorker building in Yaletown, making this unit a true gem. Boasting a spacious open floor-plan, this loft features stunning exposed brick walls, terracotta tiled floors, floor-to-ceiling windows, and sandblasted timber beams. This large 1 bedroom (current configuration) has had many updates over the years, including an air-conditioner and high end kitchen appliances. A new communal rooftop deck space with gas BBQ makes this unit a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of central Yaletown. This loft comes complete with 1 underground parking spot and storage - a rarity in this building. (29265383)

PublicRemarks: You'll love this 2 bed+den 2 bath townhome in Kitchener Mews. 1 of just 10 units in this boutique building right off The Drive, one of Vancouver's most vibrant neighbourhoods. The stylish living room and kitchen features stainless steel appliances, custom back-painted glass back splash and an island with bar seating. You'll love the city and mountain views. In-suite laundry, storage locker, bike room and underground parking. Pets and Rentals allowed. First showing at open house Feb 24 and 25 from 2-4pm. (29379097)

PublicRemarks: In Gastown, this ground level 989 sq ft Cordova St facing retail live / work unit is located in Koret Lofts, a historical brick and beam warehouse conversion originally constructed in 1906. The entire building has been completely rehabilitated and modernized in 2006 with all new mechanical and electrical building system components. The space showcases turn of the century architectural and structural design with exposed fir beams, stone and a concrete wall. The area comprises 705 sq ft of ground level space with a retail storefront beneath 18' ceilings, a rear kitchen, and an additional 284 sq ft of upper mezzanine area with a 3 piece bathroom, plus laundry. 1 underground assigned parking stall is included. An exciting investment opportunity with the area seeing improvements through redevelopment of Westbank's Blood Alley project, and future proposed Cohen Block by Bosa 1 block west on Cordova St. (34367681)

Furniture (inside & patio) can be sold with the unit. (29225763)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the Edge Building, an exceptional multipurpose loft building nestled on the edge of downtown. This stunning 1-bed, 2-bath loft has undergone a meticulous renovation in 2022 with sleek & modern finishes tied into the building's industrial design features. Upon entering, you'll note the 15-foot ceilings, which combined with the large windows & open layout, bathe the space in natural light. The enclosed bedroom on the upper level provides a serene space with a spa-like ensuite. Immerse yourself in panoramic views of the city skyline & ocean from your private balcony. Residents of the Edge Building have access to multiple amenities, including a gym, music room, metal/wood shop, & pottery studio. Plenty of in-unit storage & an underground parking stall. (29280666)

PublicRemarks: This home has a prime location, right behind Robson Street, in walking distance to all the luxury shopping, fine dining and the downtown business district. The layout is perfect. This N/E corner suite has lots of windows to enjoy the warm morning sun but avoids the extreme summer heat. The view into the downtown core is simply amazing, especially at night.  Two large bedroom, each with their own full bathroom and the Master Bedroom large enough to accomodate a King Size bed. They are wisely separated, to provide complete privacy. Two U/G parking stalls are included and so is a storage unit. The building features a number of amenities, including a gym, sauna, party room and even a workshop. If of interest to the purchaser, most of the chattels are available to purchase and can be included. (29188654)

PublicRemarks: It's a very bright, family home at The Madison, in the heart of Kits!! With 2 large size bdrm & spacious office that can be considered as a 3rd bdrm. In primary bdrm with 3-piece ensuite king-size bed fits easily; In the 2nd bdrm you may fit queen-size bed. PublicRemarks: This is an open concept 2 bedrooms, 2 baths corner unit with solarium, den, provide a super view of downtown and BC stadium. Excellent investment. (29225786)

PublicRemarks: The Arbutus! Located in Kitsilano and a 5-minute walk to the future Arbutus Skytrain Station. Designed by NSDA Architects & Cristina Oberti Interior Design, this concrete boutique building comprises 20 beautifully designed homes. This 639SF 1 bed / bath + den features imported Italian Scavolini kitchen cabinetry, under cabinet LED lighting, quartz countertops, Miele integrated appliances, 4 burner gas cooktop, self-cleaning wall oven, speed oven, built-in fridge/freezer and full size DW. Expansive 9' ceilings & oversized windows provide naturally lit interiors. Exquisite wall-to-wall European hardwood floors throughout. All-season climate control with energy-efficient solar shading and air-conditioning for year round comfort. Too many features to list! (28997835)

PublicRemarks: This customized character loft is a rare find in the heart of Gastown! Enjoy a flexible layout with endless options set in stylish exposed brick walls, lustrous concrete flooring, large picture windows, original timber beams, unique restoration style bookshelf/library, large storage space, and several fine touches that provide a unique and modern feel. A sleek kitchen lines one wall, lending to the sense of openness. Nicely updated throughout in 2020. Two commercial BBQ areas located in the courtyard, perfect for entertaining. The highly coveted Koret Lofts is located near several popular restaurants and bars, shopping, transit, and a short walk to Canada Place, Waterfront Station, and all the eclectic spots in historic Gastown. (29365024)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Christenson House a piece of architectural art nestled in the historic neighbourhood of Strathcona. This Scandinavian inspired 1 Bedroom/1.5 Bathroom over 2 levels features European designed kitchen & appliances, polished concrete floors, custom white oak staircase with matching feature wall & glass railing. The Living space extends outdoors onto a covered patio & further into your fenced yard. Spacious master suite connects to walk-in closet, ensuite & private balcony overlooking the grounds. Bathrooms feature vanities, sinks & mirrors by Artelinea & in-wall toilet tank systems by Oli/Toto. Electronic blinds, flush mounted doors, magnetic Italian hardware & hidden hinges throughout add to the minimal feel & clean lines. Showings by Appointment. (29306417)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to The Opsal by Bastion Development. Stunning 2 Bedroom / 2 Bathroom corner unit with separated bedrooms and an open concept floor plan that maximizes space and natural light. The chef-inspired kitchen features a gas cooktop and stainless steel appliances. Primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and a 4 piece ensuite bathroom. Enjoy fantastic city views from your patio and the convenience of a central location near the sea wall and everything Olympic Village has to offer. Fantastic amenities including an exercise centre, bike room and steam/sauna. Unit comes with 2 parking stalls side by side and 1 storage locker. (29275486)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Green on Queensbury in Moodyville! This south-facing, 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom unit is located on the quiet side of the building, with a south facing oversized patio looking over Moodyville park. Inside, you'll find an open concept floorplan with over-height ceilings, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The integrated Fisher Paykel kitchen appliances add a touch of elegance, while the Jaga heating and cooling system ensures year-round comfort. The luxurious spa-like primary bathroom features his and her sinks, a tub with full height tile surround, and a separate shower. Additional building amenities include a fitness centre, guest suite, lounge area, and a dog wash station. Includes two parking stalls and a storage locker. Open House Sat Feb 10th 2 to 4pm. (29284165)

PublicRemarks: Bright and spacious, corner, SE facing unit w/amazing water views! This elegant 2BD/2BA plus solarium/den is located in sought after The Olympic in the heart of Lower Lonsdale. Floor to ceiling windows bring tons of natural light. Renovations in 2017 include custom kitchen, hardwood flooring, modern exposed concrete walls & ceiling, 2 newer bathrooms. 2 extra large bedrooms. Master bedroom w/ensuite and good size closet. Solarium can be used as a studio or office. Well maintained building w/gym, bike storage and lovely courtyard. Included 2 parking, 1 locker. (29258004)

Suite pre-wired for security system. (28755896)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Aqua, a fantastic development by Concord Pacific in the Beach District. This very functional two bedroom, two bathroom floor plan has ample rooms and lots of storage space. Brand new flooring throughout, blinds, and kitchen have all been modernized so all you need to do is bring your furniture and move right in. Owners here have access to the Super Club which carries a phenomenal amenity set including: 80 foot indoor pool, hot tub, dry sauna, steam billiards room, theatre, guest suite, gym, children's play area and concierge. Step outside of the building and you have grocery stores, restaurants, coffee shops, George Wainborn Park, and the seawall on a short stroll away. Yaletown life is calling, and this is your opportunity to get into a great city home! (29304370)

PublicRemarks: Experience luxury living in Downtown Vancouver's Coal Harbour at West Pender's Live/Work complex. This renovated unit boasts 9 ft ceilings and an open floor plan, allowing for versatile live/work arrangements. The Italian Dada kitchen features high-end Gaggenau and Sub-Zero appliances. Recently upgraded with new floors, paint, wood-panel design, wallpapers, curtains, and lighting fixtures, the unit exudes sophistication. With Stanley Park, Robson and Granville Strips, and the seawall just steps away, this space offers both convenience and luxury. Make it yours today! (29344027)

PublicRemarks: Spectacular water view of English Bay and Granville Island this is luxury 2 bed, 2bath plus office/den and a spacious balcony unit in Tate. Designed by award-winning Merrick Architecture, "private collection" is only applied from level 32 to the top. This unit has central A/C, high ceiling, heated bathroom floors, spa-like lavish bathroom finishes, European appliances by Miele and Bosch. 2 parking spots and a locker! Fantastic location for restaurants, shopping and entertainment. The building has over 11,700 sq feet of indoor and outdoor amenities, and 5200 square ft garden. (29218528)

PublicRemarks: PENTHOUSE LIVING! A gorgeous UPDATED SW CORNER suite with PANORAMIC CITY VIEWS incl False Creek, Burrard Inlet & Mountains features 2 SEPARATED bedrooms (for privacy), 2 baths, GLASS SURROUNDED OPEN DEN (great for an OFFICE w/VIEWS), newly installed AIR CONDITIONING, BALCONY, over sized windows, kitchen with gas stove, stone counter-top, in-suite FLEX rm and in-suite laundry. 5 star building amenities incl concierge service, swimming pool, hot tub, steam, sauna, media rm, clubhouse, gym and yoga rm. Conveniently located to the MARINASIDE SEAWALL, Urban Fare, Starbucks, fine eateries, ROUNDHOUSE CANADA LINE STATION, Yaletown's boutique shopping, David Lam Park, George Wainborn Park all minutes away! Includes 1 PARKING & 1 LOCKER. Open House Sat/Sun Feb 17/18th 2-4pm (29359660)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Kitsilano! This stunning 2 bed 2 bath+ den in The Pulse boasts an unbeatable location nestled in the vibrant Kitsilano neighbourhood. The open concept layout creates the perfect blend of comfort and sophistication. The south-facing orientation fills the home with natural light and provides a picturesque and quiet outlook onto a school. The space features a gourmet kitchen with S/S appliances and large island, a spacious patio and a large primary bedroom with walk-in closet and luxurious ensuite bathroom. Plenty of storage space including a large den and 1 storage  locker. 2 PARKING STALLS! Just steps from grocery stores, transit options, upcoming Broadway skytrain, schools, recreation facilities and Arbutus Walk. Open House Sat Feb 3rd 2-4PM. (29258041)

PublicRemarks: Welcome home to this beautiful 2 Bedroom & 2 Bathroom home w/beautiful City & Water views nestled in the highly sought after Lower Lonsdale. This spacious home offers a desirable layout w/both bedrooms on either side separated by the spacious Kitchen (w/Quartz Counters throughout & Premium Stainless Steel Appl) & open concept Living, Dining Rooms which is large enough to host all your big gatherings & can also extend onto the balcony which overlooks the City, Water and Waterfront Park. The large primary bedroom offers a spacious layout complete with a 5 piece Spa-Like Ensuite w/bench seating in the shower and a Master walk-in Closet. The 2nd bathroom offers a Tub & Shower. This home comes with 2 parking spots, 1 Storage Locker, Fitness Studio & Social Lounge. Rentals and Pet friendly. (29335434)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Kiki On Duke. A timeless collection of eight brand new 3 bedroom boutique townhomes in the heart of Norquay Village. Luxurious finishes and modern designs, featuring spacious and open floor plans. Gourmet chef kitchens with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops. Plenty of built in storage and closet organizers. On a quiet tree lined street, steps away from transit, shopping and amenities. Very desirable neighborhood. (29103256)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to The Camellia - a solid concrete building located in the heart of Vancouver West. Luxurious features include 10' ceilings throughout, engineered hardwood flooring, deep soaker tubs, Hydronic heating/cooling system and Miele Appliances (kitchen exhaust vent, fridge, gas stove, oven, microwave & DW). This bright SE facing home presents an efficient layout with separated bedrooms for added privacy. It comes with 1x parking spot & 1x storage locker. A stone's throw from Langara-49th Canada Line station, Oakridge Centre, Langara College, and Langara Golf Course. School catchment: Annie B Jamieson Elementary & Sir Winston Churchill Secondary. (29151227)

PublicRemarks: Offering a bright two-bedroom and two-bathroom corner suite with gorgeous views of False Creek and David Lam Park! This 1156 square foot home is move-in ready or can be used as a blank canvas to unleash your creativity and bring your dream-home ideas to fruition. Featuring a desirable floorplan, spacious rooms throughout, a bright solarium that is perfect for a home office, a large den for more storage space, a private kitchen with huge windows and beautiful water views that can be enjoyed from the sunny southwest facing living room. 'Parkview Tower' offers a fantastic amenities package that include an indoor swimming pool, hot tub, sauna, exercise room, caretaker, and a courtyard. Situated in the heart of Yaletown - with the False Creek seawall and David Lam Park across the street, and just one block from award-winning restaurants, boutique shops, trendy cocktail bars and more! Open Houses: Thursday, February 15th from 4:30-6pm; Saturday, February 17th & Sunday, February 18th from 11am-1pm (29343106)

PublicRemarks: This stunning, SW corner 2 bed + den, 2 bathroom home epitomizes elevated luxury urban living! This renovated home, perched on the 33rd floor features a sophisticated renovation including A/C, motorized blinds, new appliances, designer flooring, bathroom glass enclosures and California Closets built-ins. Appreciate an oversized balcony offering panoramic marina and cityscape vistas. The functional floorplan offers separated bedrooms for ultimate privacy, open concept kitchen with island seating, living and dining rooms and floor to ceiling windows. 5 star hotel inspired amenities include concierge, pool, fitness centre, hot tub, steam, sauna, media room, clubhouse and yoga room. Steps from the Seawall and the city's best downtown offerings! *OPEN HOUSE: SAT FEB 10 4 2-4PM* (29304282)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Dunbar at 39th by Wesgroup. Designed by Taizo Yamamoto, this concrete boutique building offers 29 beautifully designed 1, 2 & 3 bedroom homes & City Homes of up to 1,700 SQ FT. PublicRemarks: Welcome to Ashton! Fairborne's first chapter in the Lynn Creek Village community. Our E-plan is a perfectly laid out, northeast facing, corner 3 bedroom home facing the park and greenbelt. This premium collection of 140 residences is showcased over two 6-storey buildings capturing the spirit of North Shore living. Enjoy Samsung smart technology stainless steel appliance package, quartz countertops, laminate wood flooring & 9' ceilings. Heating & cooling provided by heat pump. Amenities include a social lounge, bike repair & wash, pet wash, meeting rooms. Bordered by upcoming expansion of Marie Park Place and new Greenbelt. Walking distance to many great restaurants, shops & breweries & transit. (29078698)

PublicRemarks: Kensington Gardens by premiere developer Westbank.  This bright and spacious south facing, concrete townhome has 2 bedroom plus den and a huge 292 square ft south facing private patio great for outdoor entertaining. Includes 1 parking and one large storage locker. PublicRemarks: FREEHOLD CORNER UNIT T/H in Aspenwood, Champlain Heights. Private front and back yards on a quiet street, yet close to transit. Laminated floor on main and basement, carpet in bedrooms and stairs. 3 good size bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms upstairs. Living room, dinning room, eating area, kitchen and a powder room on main floor. Huge recreation room, laundry and 2 covered parking stalls in basement level. Property has been well kept by present owners for the last 23 years, newer appliances & furnace. Walking distance to Cook Elementary, Champlain Heights Park, Captain Cook Park, Champlain Heights Community Centre, few minutes driving to Everett Crowley Park, Killarney Secondary and Fraserview Golf Course. Accepted offer. (29339725)

PublicRemarks: Nestled in the heart of Downtown Vancouver, this extraordinary 2-bed, 2-bath Sub-penthouse residence is a true gem. Situated on the lively and opulent Alberni Street, just a stone's throw from the bustling Robson shopping district, it epitomizes urban luxury living. Immerse yourself in the allure of this fully upgraded unit, boasting a contemporary and streamlined design with an expansive, open layout. Revel in brand-new appliances, including in-suite laundry, a chic kitchen island, state-of-the-art AC and heating systems, and two generous sized covered balconies that add a lavish touch to the nearly 1,000 sqft interior. Indulge in the opulence of the building's amenities, which include an indoor pool and hot tub for unwinding, a soothing sauna, a well-equipped gym, and an outdoor communal patio area adorned with BBQs and dining spaces. Additionally, this unit comes with one coveted parking stall. The icing on the cake: the building welcomes short term rental, allowing you to turn your investment into profit! (28917069)

PublicRemarks: Experience the perfect blend of history and modernity at Garage in Gastown! This 2-bed/2-bath gem, meticulously renovated, offers the best of both worlds. Originally constructed in 1890 as the Canada Cordage Co., and later expanded in 1930 as the Nagle Brothers garage, this space seamlessly fuses the past with the present. As part of Salient's visionary mixed-use redevelopment, Garage stands as a testament to urban innovation. From the rejuvenated retail and office spaces to the addition of contemporary residential floors centered around the charming GaolerÂ´s Mews courtyard, it's a masterpiece of design. Completed in 2009, Garage received the prestigious 2010 UDI Award of Excellence in Urban Development for "Best Heritage," solidifying its status as a historic marvel turned modern wonder. Don't miss the opportunity to call Garage home and be a part of Gastown's rich history. Live, work, and thrive in a space that embodies the best of Salient's warehouse conversions. Discover urban living like never before. (29272309)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the Tate, perfectly located in the downtown core. This luxury residence is on the 40th floor boasts coveted southwest exposure with stunning mountain & water views, and an abundance of natural lights. 2-bed 2-bath + den/3rd bed, a testament to exquisite design featuring central A/C, 9' ceilings & radiant heat in bathroom. Walking distance to Yaletown sky train Station & all the hot spots in Yaletown. 1 parking & 1 locker included. Great rental income at $4,800/m. Open house on Feb. 18 from 1-2:30pm. (29354987)

PublicRemarks: A family-sized space in the heart of it all! This sought-after 3-bed, 2-bath corner unit provides 1164 Sqft of functional floorplan with bright and open living space,  generously sized bedrooms, laundry room & ample storage. Unwind or entertain on your sunny wrap-around patio & indulge in added privacy from your bonus 2nd patio attached to the primary bedroom. Recent suite updates include fresh paint, new lighting, kitchen upgrades & in-floor heating in both bathrooms. Nestled on a tranquil street just a short stroll from Trout Lake, Laura Secord Elementary, Commercial/Broadway Station & the vibrant shops, dining and bustling community of Commercial Drive. These 3 bedroom units are truly a rare offering and a perfect townhouse alternative. 2 parking, 1 storage & 1 pet allowed. Come see! (29279915)

PublicRemarks: Rarely available!! Fantastic top floor condo in prime Kitsilano location at Henley Park. North of 4th Avenue between Yew and Vine, right on the crest. Beautiful, panoramic water, mountain and city views! 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, 826 square ft living area plus very large balcony. Bright and quiet with good efficient floorplan. North facing onto nice, tree-lined street. The kitchen, bathroom and flooring were updated in 2013 and the unit was just freshly painted. Features include vaulted ceilings, several skylights, gas fireplace, crown mouldings, wainscoting, parking stall and storage locker. Bonus feature is a common roof-top deck with stunning views! Perfect neighbourhood, just steps from shops, restaurants, school, parks and beach. (29286067)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Harbour Cove! An exceptional 2-bed, 2-bath False Creek condo, offering 1300sf of living space in a well-maintained concrete building. As you enter, you'll be captivated by the bright & open layout. One of the highlights is the large solarium, perfect for a home office while overlooking the city, ocean & mountains. Indulge in the excellent amenities, including an indoor pool, gym, hot tub, & concierge. Nestled within the heart of False Creek, this condo offers a private setting, while still remaining conveniently located. Take a stroll to W 4th shops, enjoy a day at Kits Beach, or explore the shops at Granville Island, all just a short walk away. Additionally, the easy access to the Burrard St Bridge is perfect for individuals working downtown. Ample in unit storage as well as 1 storage locker & 1 parking stall. (29312661)

PublicRemarks: Your move in ready dream loft awaits! PublicRemarks: MIRABEL by MARCON - where beach tranquility and convenience converge. This stunning home is punctuated by superior design, luxury finishes and a functional floorplan. The chic kitchen features Sub-Zero/Wolf appliances, custom cabinetry and sleek counters, flowing on elegant hardwood flooring into the open dining and living rooms, perfect for dinner parties and movie nights. Tucked away are 2 private bedrooms and the bathroom which features floor to ceiling tiling, Brizzo matte black fixtures, intricate marble shower tiling and a rich wood vanity with ample storage. Appreciate air-conditioning, roller blinds and thoughtful designer details throughout! All of this steps to the beach, Stanley Park and the city's best eateries and shopping. Includes 1 EV ready parking & 1 XL storage locker. (29328928)

PublicRemarks: With a coveted location on Beach Avenue, this well-appointed 2 bedroom and 2 bathroom home is equipped with remarkable English Bay and sunset views. Upon entering, you will be captivated by the open-concept layout, where natural light cascades through expansive floor-to-ceiling window, creating a seamless transition between the indoor and balcony. Wake up to incredible views of the water whilst you enjoy your morning coffee and take in all the sights and sounds of city living. Located in the vibrant neighbourhood of Yaletown, you'll have easy access to an abundance of upscale boutiques, trendy restaurants, and chic cafes. Take a leisurely stroll along the seawall, relishing in the breathtaking vistas of False Creek and/or English Bay (29259834)

PublicRemarks: Welcome home to Marinaside Resort! Located in one of Vancouver's most vibrant neighbourhoods, this 2 bedroom + DEN home features floor to ceiling windows and views of the City & False Creek. Updated stove and fridge, along with hardwood flooring, this home just needs a few small touches to make it your own. Building amenities include, 24 hr concierge, indoor pool, hot tub, steam room, full gym, library, games room and party lounge. With neighbourhood amenities like, restaurants, cafe's, grocery store, and Yaletown shopping right at your doorstep, you won't find a more convenient location. Just picture yourself here..... now call for your private showing! OPEN HOUSE: SUN, FEB 11, 12-2PM (29330393)

PublicRemarks: A most impressive and unique unit to hit the market - for the first time ever. Original owners in the prestigious 888 Beach complex are ready to say goodbye. As the very first owners to move into the complex they have carefully curated a home that is difficult to come across these days. Nothing run of the mill here, from the wall papered foyer to the distinctive fireplace surround, this unit deserves a discerning Buyer. Excellent separation of bedrooms with an oversized ensuite in the primary and a generous second off the other bedroom. Floor to ceiling windows in the L/R offer a lovely view over False Creek as does the balcony. Pro-active Strata with an experienced and knowledgeable Council who ensure nothing is overlooked. 2 prkng + storage! OH Sat/SuN FEB.16/17 2-4PM (29245422)

PublicRemarks: Extremely Rare 3-Bedroom Corner Unit in Prestigious 'Venus,' Coal Harbour with Renovations and Breathtaking Views! This NE corner suite boasts 9ft ceilings, an abundance of natural light, vinyl flooring, and a newly designed gourmet kitchen with all new appliances. The entire interior has been freshly painted, and the open floorplan includes a flexible office space. Venus offers an array of amenities, including 3 elevators, a 24-hour concierge, 2 guest suites, an indoor pool, a gym, saunas, Jacuzzi, and a spacious party room. The unit features a balcony, a parking space, and a storage locker. Situated conveniently close to downtown, the Seawall, Stanley Park, Robson Street, shopping, and an array of restaurants, this property is a true gem." (29071693)

PublicRemarks: Introducing Ardea, Wesgroup's first waterfront residences in River District. This 3-bed home features over 9 ceilings, floods of natural light, & luxe amenities, setting a new River District standard. Revel in bedroom perks like built-in shelving & blackout blinds. PublicRemarks: Woodwards by Westbank. This luxury home features one of the most sought after 2 Bed & 2 Bath floor plans with unobstructed views of the North Shore Mountains. Home comes with natural stone countertops & hardwood flooring throughout, with premium wool carpets in the primary. Each bedroom is custom fitted by California Closets with automated Lutron smart blackout roller blinds. The updated kitchen has Fisher & Paykel dishwashers, a new sink and faucet. Both bathrooms are fully renovated and no expense has been spared. Amenities include: 24/hr concierge, access to Club W - world-class 2 level clubhouse with a fully equipped gym, hot tub, lounge, communal BBQ area & patio and media room. BONUS: 2 LARGE PARKING SPOTS INCLUDED. This home has it all! (29307266)

PublicRemarks: 1/2 Duplex, 2 blocks off Commercial Drive in an original 1910 built home, now converted to a duplex.  Construction is 100% complete and stratification is weeks away. On a quiet tree lined street, perfect for a young family with open concept kitchen/living/dining on the main floor and 2 large bedrooms below.  Hydronic baseboard heat, hot water on demand and vinyl plank flooring throughout. Heated floors downstairs will keep you warm and cozy. Ceiling height on the main floor is over 9 feet and 8 feet six inches below.  The exterior features cladding of original wooden shakes and new James Hardie siding.  Walk to Skytrain, restaurants, shops and parks. Schools are close by. (29133919)

PublicRemarks: Granville at 70th by West bank. Bright Southwest corner unit. 2 bedrooms/2 baths + office/den & an in-suite storage/flexi. Conveniently located next to Safeway which makes daily grocery shopping easy. Close to Richmond & YVR Airport. Downtown is about 15 minutes drive. School catchment: Dr R E McKechnie Elementary & Magee Secondary. Amenities include gym, sauna, lounge, theatre & rooftop garden. Open House Sun, Nov 12th from 2 pm to 4 pm. (28819038)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to JOYCE!! World famous developer, Westbank has done it again w/this incredible project. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom + storage room home perched up on the 8th floor honing a Northeast exposure with views all the way to Burrard Inlet features A/C, integrated appliances by Miele and Bosch, Italian porcelain tiles throughout and an oversized balcony. Sleek matte black fixtures and TRIPLE-glazed windows will ensure peace and quiet in this ever-growing Collingwood neighbourhood. Rooftop amenities include, private study rooms, cherry blossom garden, gym, library, party lounge and tons of outdoor area. Mere steps away from the skytrain station for easy access to Metrotown, Crystal Mall, & Station Square. Also comes with ---TWO--- parking stalls and a storage locker!! (29236285)

PublicRemarks: This stunning 2-bedroom + den suite at 2550 Garden Drive features 887 sqft of open and light filled space. Incredible construction quality from trusted Developer Bucci Developments. Spacious and thoughtfully designed kitchen with premium integrated Fulgor & Milano appliances, wood cabinets and quartz counter. Further features include A/C, HRV system, 9' ceilings, engineered white oak floors, ample storage solutions, built-in laundry station, custom front entry storage niche, roller-shades, USB outlets and more! Just steps to Nanaimo St and Commercial Dr., Trout Lake Park and Commercial-Broadway Skytrain. Amenities include a social lounge, expansive outdoor terrace, garden plots and children's play area. One parking and a storage locker included! Schedule your viewing today! (29317053)

PublicRemarks: The Bel Air - A highly sought-after, well maintained, CONCRETE, boutique Art Deco building in a prime Kitsilano location. TOP FLOOR unit with functional & ideal floorplan: 2 large separated beds & baths, 9 ft ceilings, generous living & dining space,North-facing, large windows provides lots of natural light, charming balcony, huge in-suite storage & Bonus office/solarium. Walking distance to all necessities including public transit (soon to have Arbutus Station skytrain), Arbutus Greenway, Parks, schools, restaurants, shopping, and kits beach. 1 underground parking & 1 storage included. Pet & Rental friendly. Viewing by appointment only. (29058357)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the Crystallis! A centrally located residential tower close to shopping, recreation, and public transit. This 2-bedroom 2-bathroom unit features a large patio with beautiful water and city views. There is potential to purchase the neighboring unit as well and combine the two units to create your own 4-bedroom home in the sky. There is already access between units 1602 & 1603. The unit is in original condition and could be renovated to feature your ideas! Unit 1602 also listed R2842801. (29272315)

PublicRemarks: Nestled on the 20th floor, this rarely available well maintained 2-bedroom boutique condo in Yaletown offers breathtaking views and an unbeatable location. Whether move-in ready or a canvas for your renovation ideas, this quiet sub-penthouse just off Marinaside and Drake presents an open floor plan with views from every window. Step out onto the spacious patio to enjoy unobstructed views over David Lam Park and False Creek, providing the perfect setting for al fresco living. Enjoy the convenience of being steps from Elsie Roy Elementary, David Lam Park, Urban Fare, the Roundhouse, and the Sea Wall, placing you at the heart of Yaletown's dynamic lifestyle. (29303576)

PublicRemarks: 828 Harbourside Drive is a premium office building first constructed in 2005 . This building has attractive landscaping and architecture that is situated along the North Shore Spirit Trail, providing great pedestrian and bicycle access . PublicRemarks: Welcome to Tribeca Lofts, steps from Yaletown's popular shops and restaurants! Tastefully updated , New open Euro-style Kitchen blended into Living/Dining with high-end Bosch appliances and quartz counter tops . New Engineer hardwood flooring throughout in the unit. Living room features a cozy gas F/P & a window seat looking over False Creek, the marina and beautiful fountain garden . Steps away from the Seawall, Granville Island ferry, English Bay and newly developed shopping area . Huge master bdrm features walk-in closet & deluxe spa style bath with jetted tub & separate shower. Superbly managed building with 24 hrs concierge, swimming pool, sauna, gym and manicured court yard. Pets and rental friendly. (29304391)

PublicRemarks: PERFECT LOCATION! Stunning apartment at the heart of Vancouver. This well-maintained 2 bed + den includes 2 bathrooms; a large living and dining area; complete kitchen with a gas stove, full-sized fridge, and dishwasher; in-suite laundry; and a large storage room. The entire unit is surrounded by floor-to-ceiling windows, allowing you to enjoy panoramic views of the mountains, False Creek, and the city. TRANSIT AND WALKING-FRIENDLY, everything is only steps away. INVESTMENT ALERT! The new Broadway Skytrain expansion will be only minutes away, with the new station located close by the complex. (28980745)

PublicRemarks: Experience the luxurious lifestyle at THE NEW YORKER in Arbutus Walk, Kitsilano's exclusive community. Enjoy sweeping park views, serene gardens, and peaceful spots for reading and sipping coffee. This unit boasts elegant flooring, large windows, and natural light. The kitchen features maple cabinets, granite counters, a breakfast bar, and new stainless steel appliances. A walk-in pantry adds convenience. Updates include fresh paint and modern lighting throughout. Built by Bastion Developments, this unit has 9' ceilings for a spacious feel. The primary bedroom accommodates a king bed and has an ensuite shower. The Dining/Living area offers a gas fireplace and balcony overlooking the park. Walk to Connaught Park, private school, and high school. Close to community center, transit, skytrain, bike share, cafes, restaurants, and shopping. Includes bike room, meeting room, and 2 covered parking spaces. 2 cats or 1 dog allowed. (29331766)

PublicRemarks: La Mirada in prestigious Point Grey I Jericho. Enjoy the home's townhome feel with direct access to the tree lined street. Corner unit with North/East exposure. Expansive 230+ SF patio with 2 private gardens great for entertainment & pets. Recent updated bath, hardwood floors & mirrored wall. L-shape Kitchen boast stainless steel appliance, bright window for plenty of natural light & air flow. Open living & dining area with gas fireplace, glass sliding door & unique high corner windows. Spacious primary bedroom with his & her closets, built-in shelving & desk area and an ensuite with full sized walk-in shower & window for even more daylight. 2nd bdrm has mirror sliding closet doors, track lighting & generous sized window. Convenient insuite storage & laundry. 2 parking with own bike rack lockup (29334104)

PublicRemarks: West Coast lifestyle! This bright & spacious 2 bed, 2 full bath home in luxurious CONCRETE building by ANTHEM offers fantastic layout & elegant interior design w/engineered hard.flrs, AC & quartz countertops. Large open concept kitchen feat full size, top of the line Bosh applins, great storage & gas range. Principal bed feat walk-in closet, deluxe spa-like ensuite w/large walk-in shower,his & her sinks & heated flrs. Bedrms don't share walls & are nicely separated for privacy. Large balcony w/natural gas & hose hookups extends living space w/sweeping views of NS mounts. Separate laundry rm w/tons of storage.Bonus TWO PARKING STALLS & THREE STORAGE LOCKERS! Amazing location in coveted Lower Lonsdale, ideally situated walking distance to SeaBus, parks & trendiest eateries & local shops. Open House, Saturday, January 20th, 1-3pm (29258777)

PublicRemarks: WATERFRONT GROUND FLOOR UNIT + LARGE PATIO! Waterfront living at Cascade at the Pier in this beauty 1-bed, 1-bath + flex space/closet unit. This unit has air conditioning, & features hardwood flooring, Italian Scavolini kitchen, Bosch appliances. This stunning unit faces the court yard for private entering on the 468 square foot patio. This unit specifically offers 10 foot ceilings and is fitted with a direct gas line for your outdoor fire pit & BBQ in your private waterfront garden oasis. Take advantage of the exclusive Pinnacle hotel facilities, such as the fitness centre, pool, hot tub, and sauna/ steam room. Homeowners get special VIP privileges.1 parking and 1 storage locker. (29138892)

PublicRemarks: VIEWS VIEWS VIEWS! PROMENADE by POLYGON, located in the heart of Lower Lonsdale. This rarely available One Bedroom & Den suite features: upscale finishes throughout - breathtaking SOUTHWEST ocean, city and mountain view.  Airconditioned, high-quality engineered wood flooring, integrated cabinetry, 5-burner gas range, large windows throughout. Sunset views and picturesque Lions Gate Bridge in bustling Lower Lonsdale amenities. Key feature - spacious patio over 310 sqft. 1 parking 1 storage locker. Amenities include outdoor rooftop deck w/bbq and pet wash station. Within steps to the Pier, festivals, museums, the Shipyards, popular cuisines, shop at the Quay. PublicRemarks: Experience breathtaking water, city, and mountain views from this exceptionally spacious and well-designed 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom unit crafted by Bosa. The entrance and kitchen area boast hardwood flooring, complemented by granite kitchen counters, a gas range, and a gas fireplace. Step out onto the expansive balcony to relish the stunning surroundings. The building is equipped with amenities such as a pool, hot tub, sauna, gym, and recreational room. The unit includes two generously sized secured parking spaces and a separate spacious storage locker. Immerse yourself in the vibrant urban lifestyle of Vancouver's fastest-growing area, complete with entertainment and convenience. Open house: Feb 17, 2-4pm. (29333118)

PublicRemarks: Introducing Format by Cressey ' a 13-storey mixed use development situated at the high-profile corner of Dumfries and Kingsway. PublicRemarks: Two complimentary Vancouver-based schools that provide a dynamic educational program for pre-school and elementary students. The schools, with owner controlled real estate assets, have been in operation for 20+ years with carefully curated teachers and a value-add based curriculum built on constant improvement. No enrollment marketing has been required for the last 15+ years as its largely by referral and word of mouth - a true testament to the quality of education and owner care. The owners are seeking sale or partnership opportunities to expand their operations, and continue the well-established, child-centric educational programming within a rapidly growing community for future generations. (34027756)

PublicRemarks: One of the best buildings in Vancouver. The ARC - by Concord Pacific is one of the newest Prestigious Iconic building at the gateway of Downtown False Creek. This Luxurious 2 Br + Den with large balcony. It offers timeless & quality finishing. Kitchen and all appliances by Miele. Engineered quartz stone countertop, Marble backsplash. EV charging. PublicRemarks: The perfectly unique, park facing one bedroom & den you've been waiting for. Welcome to the rarely available, two-story condo at Eden by Bosa. Enjoy elevated condo living with a townhome feel. PublicRemarks: Great value! Beautiful 3 bd/2 bth renovated 2-level bright townhome close to UBC. Gorgeous kitchen features 5-burner gas stove, SS appliances & white granite counters. The living rm features a cozy fireplace & is big enough to fit a grand piano! Enjoy ur fruit garden & ur sunny South-facing private patio. 1 Bed on Main with 2 LARGE bdrms upstairs & a lovely solarium. Sep. entrances for both levels makes it great for homestay students/all family members. In-suite laundry in flex room. Lots of built-in storage. Radiant in-floor heating thruout. Building features: events room, children's room, fitness room, workshp, bike room, laundry facilities, car-wash station with hot water & a fabulous rooftop deck with sweeping mntn VIEWS. Unit has 1 undergrnd parkg, 1 storage locker. Strata fees cover water, heat, cooking. A great community-minded buildg with friendly neighbours. Pet-friendly. Conventional financing available on remaining 47yr lease. Walkscore 98! Close to beaches, shops, UBC, DT. A must-see lifestyle GEM in Kits! (29266933)

PublicRemarks: Introducing La Vista, a contemporary masterpiece meticulously crafted by Formwerks Boutique Properties. This mixed-use gem boasts 13 residential units and 3 commercial units, harmoniously blending elegance and functionality. Ideally situated on the corner of 14th Avenue and Arbutus Street, this 8-year-old architectural marvel defines modern living on Vancouver's prestigious west side. Explore the ideal business setting at 3038 Arbutus Street, featuring a 666 sqft commercial space with coveted C2 zoning. The warm shell condition provides a versatile canvas for diverse business ventures, complemented by high ceilings, expansive frontage and glazing, and convenient load access. Take advantage of the head start for customization with access to electrical, plumbing, natural gas services and venting. Additionally, the unit includes 1 secure underground parking stall, making it an excellent investment property and an ideal choice for owner-occupiers. Welcome to a world where sophistication meets opportunity. (34564837)

PublicRemarks: Great Value! Unobstructed view of golf course and mountain. This luxury 830 sqft 2 bd 2 bath north-east corner unit on the 20 th floor.  Very sought after 03 plan in Cambie Gardens with 190 sqft wraparound balcony enjoying the fantastic view.   Engineered HW flooring, heating & cooling system, automated lighting & sleek roller shades. A gourmet kitchen includes natural stone countertops and a 30' Sub Zero + Wolf appliance package with integrated refrigerator and under counter wine fridge. A spa-inspired bathroom with marble countertops, and Nuheat flooring. Over 35,000 SF of amenities including indoor pool, spa, outdoor terrace & fitness centre. 1 parking and 1 locker. Open house: (Sat) Dec 2, 2023  at 2-4 pm. (29078399)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Winona on Cambie, an intimate collection of parkside luxury residences built to LEED Gold standards. Led by award winning GBL Architects w/modern interiors by Portico Design, you will immediately feel elevated in this stunning 3BED, 2BATH w/FLEX home. Offering a family sized kitchen inc high end full size WOLF gas cooktop/wall oven, SUBZERO fridge, polished Cambria quartz w/waterfall edge, modern duo tone cabinetry & plenty of island seating. Easterly facing living room & covered patio w/quiet outlook and side access. ENG HW, AC, HRV, 9Â´ ceilings, roller blinds & spa-inspired baths w/mood lighting makes this home a GEM. Minutes to Oakridge, QE Park, Marine Gateway (T&T), Langara & short walk to Marine Drive SkyTrain. Catchment - Wilfred Laurier Elementary & Churchill Secondary. (29259455)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Ava, a boutique collection of 35 thoughtfully crafted 1 to 3 bed homes in the heart of Oakridge located just steps to the Canada Line, UBC bus, Langara college, golf course & Oakridge mall. PublicRemarks: The NEW YORKER at Arbutus Walk! Bright 2 Bdrm, 2 bathroom + flex space with Park and mountain views. PublicRemarks: Welcome to 'BROOK' in the OlympicVillage. This end and corner unit features 2 separate bedrooms with ensuites, a super-wide hallway with ample space at the entrance, 9' ceilings, and northeast spectacular views of False Creek both day and night. Featuring open-concept kitchen with large quartz island, Wolf appliances (gas stove/oven/microwave), Fisher & Paykel dishwasher & Sub Zero fridge/wine fridge. Walk out from main living space onto oversized private N/W facing patio with mountain & city views.  Enjoy bright bedrooms, tasteful full bathrooms & convenient laundry/storage nook. Includes parking, storage locker & bike storage. Concrete building featuring excellent amenities including large well-equipped exercise centre & entertaining/outdoor space. Located in the heart of Mt. Pleasant, steps from shops, restaurants, breweries & transit. Open House - Thurs 5:30-6:30pm, Sat/Sun 2-4pm (29365706)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the Capitol Residences at 833 Seymour Street in downtown Vancouver. This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo offers a contemporary open concept layout flooded with natural light. It is move-in ready! Enjoy breathtaking views of downtown, the ocean, and mountains from the 34th floor. The unit comes with A/C, 1 large parking spot and is conveniently located near SkyTrain stations, world-class shopping and restaurants. Residents can take advantage of the 4 high-speed elevators, fitness centre, concierge service and lounge. Don't miss this opportunity to live in luxury in the heart of Vancouver. (29354941)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Pacific Point 2, located at Homer and Pacific Streets in Vancouver. Originally built in 1993, this building has undergone complete renovations in 2013 and has been fully rain-screened in 2022, including all windows. This spacious unit offers 2 bedrooms plus a den/solarium and a laundry room with storage. The primary bedroom and living room offers False Creek water views. The unit has been entirely modernized with a great kitchen, bathrooms, and high-end finishings, including Italian cabinetry and brand new top-of-the-line kitchen appliances. This unit comes with 1 parking and 1 locker. Pacific Point 2 offers a variety of amenities, including a swimming pool, gym, hot tub, and concierge services - the perfect place to call home. (29374280)

PublicRemarks: This fantastic property nestled in one of the city's most sought-after neighborhoods, Little Mountain, offering proximity to all the vibrant attractions of Main Street and Hillcrest. Spacious 2-bedroom, plus den, 2-bathroom residence is situated in "The Crest," just steps away from Queen Elizabeth Park. Boasting a generous 1,004 SqFt of indoor living space, you'll also enjoy a sizable 254 SqFt western-exposed patio. The open and inviting floor plan features wide plank flooring, 9-foot ceilings, and an abundance of windows for natural light. The chef's kitchen is well-appointed with stainless steel appliances, The primary bedroom provides ample closet space and a luxurious ensuite bathroom. Notably, this unit offers dual entrances and secured underground parking. (29285427)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the Private Residences of Hotel Georgia. This rarely available 1-bed unit has stunning design features including a mahogany veneer door, custom cabinetry, open concept kitchen, and a luxurious spa-like bathroom with marble countertops and shower wall. This home features 9'5 foot ceilings and an abundance of natural lighting to show off the gourmet kitchen features Miele appliances, a built-in coffee maker, and custom oak cabinetry. Enjoy A/C and heating via a geothermal system  system and amenities like a 24hr concierge, indoor spa, and gym that are shared with the Rosewood Hotel. Experience downtown living at its finest with shops, cafes, and restaurants at your doorstep. Book your private tour now for a glimpse of luxury and convenience. (29330450)

PublicRemarks: This elegantly renovated two-storey townhome boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, & a butler's pantry. The open living area features a gas fireplace, while a large north-facing balcony & south-facing patio offer both relaxation & entertainment spaces. The primary bedroom is adorned with vaulted ceilings & offers peekaboo Mountain Views. Situated on a tranquil residential street, this home is just minutes away from schools, transit, shopping on Commercial Drive, & the scenic Trout Lake. Ample space & storage are found throughout. The property includes two side-by-side underground parking spots with direct access to the unit & one storage locker. Pets and rentals are permitted with restrictions. Don't miss the opportunity to make this move-in-ready home yours!  OH Sat/Sun 2-4pm (29318447)

PublicRemarks: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION! KINGCREST ESTATES is conveniently located at 28th and Knight, providing an ideal setting for small families! Quiet inner courtyard exposure coupled with the best "duplex-like unit" in the complex makes this a winner! Spacious open concept living-dining-great room space with extra high ceilings. The top floor has 2 bedrooms with vaulted ceilings and a functional jack-and-jill ensuite bathroom. The entry level has a perfect guest suite with a 3 piece bath and the LARGE ATTACHED GARAGE with its own entrance provides room for parking. Walking distance to Save-On-Foods, Vancouver Public Library, and Lord Selkirk Elementary School! Great community and neighbourhood makes this perfect fit for the growing family! Open house Feb 10 2-4pm/ Feb 11 3-5pm! (29329713)

PublicRemarks: Come visit our Air-conditioned and practical (almost 1000SF) 3Bed + Den large Corner unit - North West Facing - with floor to ceiling glass windows throughout the kitchen, living and dining area, plus Large wrap around balcony bringing in ample sunlights, magnificent city view with the beautiful north shore mountains as backdrop. Our Functional kitchen equips with high-end Miele appliances and Lots of cabinet storage, with a large kitchen island. Master Bedroom fits a King size bed, has a huge Walk-in Closet and a Double-sink 4 piece ensuite. 24hrs concierge available together with exercise centre, grand party room, and touch-less car wash. Steps away from Marine Gateway Station.  Walking distance to shopping, T&T supermarket, restaurants and entertainment. 1 EV Parking included. (29329773)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to this beautifully upgraded residence which embodies the essence of contemporary luxury living. Its refined transformation features upscale laminate flooring, heated floor tiles, quartz countertops, and high end appliances. The homeÂ´s allure has been further enhanced with customized California closets, pot lights throughout, and extra storage in the kitchen seating. The well thought out floorplan places 2 beds and 2 baths on the main level, while the second floor boasts a spacious living area, large kitchen, and dining space. Enjoy outdoor moments on two patios, one overlooking the courtyard and the other offering stunning views of the Vancouver city skyline, Burrard Inlet, and North Shore mountains. This pet and rental-friendly residence also includes 2 parking stalls. (29195871)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to one of the most luxury building in the downtown, this 2 bed + Flex. The building itself comes with many features such as smart home control, high end kitchen appliance from Gaggeneau, built in wardrobe, A/C and access to many amazing amenities such as pool, hot tub, sauna/ steam and out door terrace. The location itself is very convenient as it is just near by the Burrard bridge, Granville island and Yaletown. The unit itself has plenty outdoor area as well, as the unit patio is pretty huge as well. The unit contains 1 parking and also 1 bike storage. This is tenanted property where the tenants are extremely nice, but please do give us 48 hours notice. (29282514)

PublicRemarks: RARE street entry 2 level, 2 bedroom modern Yaletown townhome in an AIrbnb-friendly luxe tower, The Mark by Onni! Shielded by a bridge off-ramp for privacy and minimal traffic and less than 10 minutes walk to Wainborn Park, Seawall, Aquabus, Skytrain, or the heart of downtown, the lifestyle here is all about accessibility and recreation. Refreshed cabinetry and counters in the stunning peninsula kitchen, open spacious 1,290sf floorplan with lots of pantry space and storage, powder room on the main, great al-fresco patio, generous primary bedroom with w.i. closet and bright ensuite, 2nd bedroom with adjacent 2nd full bath, PETS OK (GREAT dog home!), 1 lckr and 1 prkng. Amenities in the building are IMPRESSIVE (gym, o.d. pool, hot tub, concierge/security)!!. Opens Sat/Sun Feb 24/25th 2-4pm. (29307249)

PublicRemarks: Discover the allure of this AirBNB-friendly residence boasting million-dollar vistas! Step into this spacious, air-conditioned 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom + den condo offering spectacular views of False Creek. Enjoy the thoughtful layout featuring bedrooms strategically positioned on opposite sides of the unit, an updated kitchen with exquisite quartz counters, a newer double convection oven, and an open layout perfect for hosting gatherings. The Versatile den provides ample space for added living area or a productive home office. Recent updates encompass a newer washer/dryer and upgraded bathroom/shower facilities. Embrace a car-free lifestyle with Stadium SkyTrain, T&T, Costco, Tinseltown Mall/Theatre, and the captivating False Creek Seawall just steps away. Revel in top-notch amenities including a 24-hour concierge, indoor pool, gym, steam room/sauna, party room, and a serene private courtyard. This gem comes complete with parking and includes heat within the strata fees. (29143003)

PublicRemarks: Soak in the sprawling textural city views overlooking Yaletown from the highly desired, DOMUS! Nestled in the SE corner, the natural light showcases this luxurious designer suite like no other. This 2 BR and 2 Bath home has been thoughtfully executed with its sleek, contemporary kitchen featuring a beautiful quartz island - perfect for entertaining, a generous office, plus another ample flex space -perfect as a second office or closet. Relax in your spa-like bathrooms, with accent wraparound tiles that are truly a showstopper! The principle bedroom features a walk-in closet plus additional closet systems for optimal storage, a rare gem for Downtown living. In the heart of Yaletown, enjoy the boutique condo lifestyle with complete amenities: gym, sauna/steam, lounge. 1 parking + 1 storage. (28836120)

PublicRemarks: Spacious & updated Nicola Street 2 bedroom / 2 bath, townhouse feel, condo, located just a block from the beach with a private entrance. The main floor features an entertainment area, Spanish heated tile & Caesar stone waterfall countertops in both the kitchen and balcony, with modular outdoor stainless-steel storage. An elegant walnut staircase leads to the 2nd level featuring 2 large bedrooms with hardwood floors, oversized closets. Hand crafted oak cabinetry & office space, a spacious upper deck, and a central living room fireplace with LED flush mount ceiling lights throughout. Bathrooms feature Caesar stone, Italian wall tile, and comforting heated floors. A beautiful home with quality workmanship for retirees or professionals seeking tranquility, easy access to the seawall, and utmost privacy. Over 1300 sq feet of space throughout, plus balconies to enjoy on each level. Added bike room, underground parking, and dedicated storage. (29083909)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Vancouver's Last Waterfront at Current's at Water's Edge! Spacious 1125sqft, 2 bed & den, 2 bath with unobstructed water views in Polygon's luxury concrete mid-rise development. Featuring an open floor plan, 9' ceilings, gourmet chef's kitchen w/big island & lots of storage, bedrooms w/no shared walls, extra office/den/storage, 237sqft balcony, nature and beautiful sunsets. It's all about the location and lifestyle - central location means a quick commute to Richmond, Burnaby/New West, UBC and onto the highways. Quiet neighbourhood with miles of walking trails, dog parks, & minutes from grocery, restaurants, banks. Building also comes with beautiful Roof-deck, Gym, Amenity room, Garden/Playground & live-in manager. Still under new home warranty, OPEN HOUSE SUN DEC 17th 2pm-4pm (29062398)

PublicRemarks: Stunning 3 level townhouse! Highly Desirable 5 yrs old 3 bed 3 bath move in condition townhouse, lots of windows, in vibrant Mt Pleasant area. 1 parking and tons of street parking infront, 1 bike Locker. Highly walkable. (29364977)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the Flagship by Concord Pacific, one of the most prestigious waterfront residences in all of downtown Vancouver. PublicRemarks: Own a piece of iconic architecture in South Oak. Designed by award-winning Arno Matis, Oku is zero emissions concrete construction offering 132 homes in 3 boutique buildings. PublicRemarks: Welcome to this completely updated 2 bd + flex space (office, library), 3 bath duplex-style home in a quiet, self-managed complex. Enjoy the proximity to Lonsdale Quay and all it has to offer, as well as the serenity of being far enough away to relax on this quiet, tree-lined street. With a large, south facing sundeck, bright, spacious rooms and tons of storage as well as 2 covered and secure parking spots and brand new air conditioning, it's an easy decision to make! Completely private living in a detached-like setting. Come see for yourself what it's like to live in this quiet and family friendly neighbourhood away from all the hustle and bustle! (29085422)

PublicRemarks: Paradigm at popular River District. 18th floor, 90 degree water & city view, bright & functional layout 3 bedroom plus den, 2 baths plus balcony off living room overlooking water & open view. High quality finishings with SS kitchen appliances, full size washer & dryer. Super club amenities including fully equipped exercise room & a kids' playroom, yoga & TRX room, different indoor & outdoor meeting areas for social gatherings & kids' play areas, bike storages with a repair & wash station, dog wash station, daytime concierge with parcel storage. This unit comes with 2 parking stalls including one EV charge and one spacious locker. Easy to show. (29363532)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to this NEW front DUPLEX on a quiet street in South Vancouver with lots to offer. This home features open concept Living/Dining Room, kitchen with s/s appliances, gas stove, quartz countertops, and modern acrylic cabinets.  10' on main floor & up to 9' ceilings on upper floor with amber natural lights. PublicRemarks: Regency Park - boutique adult-oriented (55+) concrete condominium in prestigious Kerrisdale neighbourhood! Well-maintained, bright, spacious 2 bdrm / 2 full baths with 1294 sqft of functional and comfortable living area overlooking an elevated city skyline, mountain and water views with SOUTH-WEST-NORTH exposure. Notable features include conventionally-designed rooms ideal for furniture placement, original h/w flooring throughout, inviting 105 sqft balcony, 2 secured underground parking stalls, and a pro-active strata building with roof (2021), elevator (2016), and plumbing upgrades. Only 2 suites per floor. No pets, external storage locker, or short term rentals. Conveniently located amongst the attractions, amenities, & conveniences offered at heart of the vibrant Kerrisdale community! (29338130)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Vancouver's iconic "The ARC" by Concord Pacific.  This spectacular South/West facing 2 Br+Den on 25th level is spacious and functionally designed with Yaletown & Marina view. High quality modern finishes with central heating and cooling system, Miele appliances, marble backsplashes, and a large balcony for your enjoyment. PublicRemarks: Welcome to Harbour Cove! A 2-bed, 2-bath False Creek condo, offering 1437sf of living space in a well-maintained concrete building. As you enter, you'll be captivated by the bright & open layout. One of the highlights is the views overlooking the city, ocean & mountains from. Indulge in the excellent amenities, including an indoor pool, gym, hot tub, & concierge. Nestled within the heart of False Creek, this condo offers a private setting, while still remaining conveniently located. Take a stroll to W 4th shops, enjoy a day at Kits Beach, or explore the shops at Granville Island. Additionally, the easy access to the Burrard St Bridge is perfect for individuals working downtown. Ample in unit storage, 1 storage locker & 1 parking stall. (29312665)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the NEW YORKER in vibrant Arbutus Walk! This impressive 2-bed+den, 984 sqft home offers comfort and style. With 9ft ceilings, gas fireplace, ample storage, and a den, it's cozy yet functional. Enjoy stunning views from the sub-penthouse level 6th. Updates include new laminated flooring, fresh paint, and a renovated bathroom. The chef inspired kitchen boasts granite countertops and modern stainless steel appliances. Surrounded by parks, shops, and eateries, it's an ideal location. Plus bike storage, and pet-friendly 1 dog or 2 cats are welcome! Live the Kitsilano lifestyle near parks, schools, and transit. Embrace the vibrant Kitsilano lifestyle with proximity to the Arbutus Greenway, Connaught Park, Kitsilano Community Centre, top-rated schools and the future Broadway Line. (29308580)

PublicRemarks: COMPLETELY RENOVATED THROUGHOUT, gorgeous half-duplex in the heart of Kitsilano. ALL NEW WINDOWS, NEW SKYLIGHTS, NEW SLIDING DOORS (2022), and NEW ROOF AND NEW BALCONY DECKS (2023). 1 bedroom plus good-size den, 2 full bathrooms, 2 balconies, and direct access to PRIVATE ATTACHED GARAGE! Features include top-of-the-line German wide-plank laminate flooring, heated bathroom floors, skylit living room with gas fireplace, and dining room with French doors opening to balcony overlooking gardens. Bright top-level ensuited bedroom opens to sunny balcony with tree-top outlook. The sleek contemporary kitchen offers Corian countertops and SS appliances. Located on a quiet tree-lined street, close to 4th Ave shops, restaurants, services, public transit, Kits Beach. OPEN SUN 2-4 or by appointment. (29368479)

PublicRemarks: Indulge in breathtaking False Creek water & city views from this upscale corner unit at THE ONE by Concord Pacific. Just minutes from Seawall Waterfront & vibrant Downtown, this south-facing residence features 2 bedrms, 2 bathrms, 2 dens offering a versatile 3rd bedroom option, plus an office space. The contemporary floor plan top-tier finishes, including air cond, hardwood floors, premium Miele stainless steel appliances. Revel in the elegance of crystal light fixtures, luxurious KOHLER bathrm amenities, mosaic marble tiles, the convenience of A/C. Step onto the BBQ balcony, enjoy seamless access to parking & storage.  Live in luxury with a five-star facility offering an outdoor glass pool & a spectacular entertainment area wi/a garden Roof deck. Additional privileges access to the 20th floor's opulent ARC Sky Club featuring a swimming pool and fitness facility. PublicRemarks: Welcome to GOVERNOR'S VILLAS in the heart of YALETOWN. This bright and spacious 2 BDRM, 2 BATH + DEN + FLEX home has beautiful views of F David Lam Park & False Creek. The open plan living area with good natural light provides a bright and spacious feel. A large and private den space that can be used as the 3rd bedroom. Resort amenities include an indoor pool, hot tub, gym, sauna, and beautiful private gardens with a 24 hr concierge. The central location is near Urban Fare, wine bars, restaurants, The Roundhouse, parks, Seawall, and transit. The building is fully rain-screened & re-piped, with updated windows and a pro-active strata. Only 2 suites per floor. Rental & Pets are OK. 2 Parkings with EV option. (29263861)

PublicRemarks: Rarely available and highly sought-after commercial live/work loft in historic Koret Lofts, a century-old, remade warehouse located in the heart of bustling Gastown. This 1,743 SF loft has those New York vibes coupled with heritage charm, offering 18' ceilings, all original fir beams, brick wall, and wood floors, as well as finished concrete throughout. Comes with in-suite laundry and one secure parking. Gastown's 'it' building, known for its tight-knit community and well-managed strata. Potential cash cow opportunity - this is one of Vancouver's few fully-approved buildings, allowing Airbnb rentals. Guests will love walking down the cobblestones to the area's highly-rated shops, restaurants, and cafes. This ground-level home has endless opportunities. (29259408)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Wall Center, where luxury meets convenience. PublicRemarks: High atop the 31st floor of Coal Harbour's Pointe Claire, there is a rarely available 3 bedroom/2 bath suite with fantastic views of Coal Harbour, the North Shore mountains and downtown. Fabulous open plan is extremely efficient and provides views from most every room. All bdrms are quite large, main has a WI closet and ensuite. Amenities inc fitness centre, pool, jacuzzi 7 sauna. PublicRemarks: Rarely available 2 bedroom + 2 bathroom Penthouse at Oscar by Bosa Properties. The south, east corner home is airy & bright & features high ceilings with floor to ceiling windows, showcasing breathtaking views of False Creek & Yaletown. Both bedrooms have ensuite bathrooms, & the primary bathroom includes a steam shower. The focal point of this property is the huge patio offering over 200 square feet of outdoor living space, perfect for entertaining & enjoying the warmer months in enviable style ... Create your very own outdoor oasis in the heart of Yaletown. Located steps from all the restaurants, coffee shops, George Wainborn Park, David Lam Park & the Seawall. Skytrain & all public transport are within easy walking distance. The Oscar features a gym & meeting/party room. Comes with Pkg. OH Sat Feb 17th 2-4pm (29240081)

PublicRemarks: PRIME LOCATION! Introducing The Sophia, a robust concrete townhome with 1,323 sq. ft. of living space tucked away just off the vibrant Main Street. PublicRemarks: Welcome to this unique 3 bed/2 bath corner unit perfectly situated in Olympic Village. The open concept living/dining area is surrounded in glass and blends seamlessly with the kitchen for convenient entertaining. Your Den is ideally located next to the kitchen, is sun-drenched & perfect as your work-from-home space. Just off of your dining area is the 75 SqFt covered patio. Additionally just behind the kitchen is an oversized walk-in pantry fully shelved with ample space for all of your storage needs. The custom detail of herringbone engineered hardwood flooring gives this home a luxuriously unique feel while keeping it warm & cozy throughout. Your master bedroom is generously sized and offers a walk-through closet detailed by CaliforniaClosets & leads into a custom bathroom with oversized double sided shower & double vanity. Your second & third bedrooms are also generously sized with plenty of natural light overlooking Crowe street. 1 Parking & 1 Locker included. Call to view today! (29006697)

PublicRemarks: Gorgeous south facing townhouse on a quiet street in Trendy East Village. Beautifully finished. 3 Bdrms, a Den with a window & 4 bathrooms. 1433SF Smart layout. PublicRemarks: THE ZONDA,One of the Unique building located close to future broadway Subway Station: this is a stunning 1 bedroom and den home (functionally 2 bedrooms)with High ceilings, large kitchen, light oak floors and amazing large 2 outdoor Patio of approximately 620sqft each. PublicRemarks: Welcome to the Vancouver House! This luxury-designed building, crafted by the renowned architect Bjarke Ingels offers an exceptional living experience. This 2b 2ba unit embodies everything you desire in your new home. Its outstanding features include a spacious balcony offering breathtaking views of Granville Island, English Bay and Cypress mountain, high-end Miele appliances, elegant plank oak flooring, Kohler fixtures, triple-glazed windows for energy efficiency, and hydronic heating and cooling for your comfort. PublicRemarks: Own a piece of iconic architecture in South Oak. Designed by award-winning Arno Matis, Oku is zero emissions concrete construction offering 132 homes in 3 boutique buildings. The superior window and wall structure is designed for energy efficiency and reduced sound transmission. All-season comfort from best-in-class VRF air-conditioning technology. Each home features luxurious interiors with a sleek gourmet kitchen equipped with quartz countertops and European stainless steel appliances. Building amenities include a fitness studio, co-working space, entertainment lounge for group gatherings. Conveniently located in a well-established Vancouver West neighbourhood with easy access to Churchill Secondary, Sir Wilfred Laurier Elementary, Oakridge Centre, YVR and downtown. www.okuliving.com. (28954276)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Marinaside! Experience unparalleled luxury in this two-bedroom, 2 bathroom & den in Yaletown's prestigious Aquarius Mews. Boasting breathtaking ocean and city views, this comer suite features spacious open concept living and a private patio overlooking the water. Perfect for those who appreciate the finer things in life, you are steps away from high-end amenities including the Seawall, Urban Fare, and exclusive dining options right below. Residents enjoy an abundance of amenities with access to a swimming pool, exercise centre, library, concierge and a serene garden with a pond. Open House Saturday February 17 from 2 to 4 included. (29355748)

PublicRemarks: Situated in the heart of Old Yaletown, this 1912 warehouse has been converted to beautiful+ spacious lofts. Bestowed by interior design & heritage awards, Del Prado is truly Vancouver's finest example of loft residences. This well-designed corner 2 bdrm/2 bath home boasts all of the luxuries: Aircon, open plan design, S/S appliances, gas range, gas fireplace, strata-titled parking stall, tilt n turn Euro windows that span the entire width of suite & allows for loads of natural light & amazing alfresco atmosphere with loads of original EXPOSED brick. PublicRemarks: Nestled in The Arc, one of Yaletown's latest developments, this residence epitomizes top-tier urban living. In a modern luxury building strategically positioned in Yaletown, the unit showcases a meticulously crafted 2-bedroom plus den layout, offering stunning westerly exposure and captivating water views. Indulge in the opulence of stainless steel appliances, sophisticated flooring, a marble bathroom, and storage. Conveniently located in the heart of the city's sports and entertainment district, and mere steps away from world-class dining and shopping in Yaletown/False Creek, this home provides unparalleled access to urban amenities. Parks, the seawall, Marinaside, schools, and other conveniences are all within a short walking distance. One parking and amazing amenities are included! (29303659)
