PublicRemarks: Unobstructed south facing park view!Corner lot! Beautiful brand new 2 level front 1/2 duplex with unobstructed south facing park view. Featuring the ideal floor plan with 3 Bedrooms and 3 Bathrooms. Once you enter the main floor you will notice 9 foot ceilings with an open concept kitchen, living room. Upstairs consists of 3 bedrooms with 2 full bathroom. More windows and lots of light due to corner unit. Desirable Knight area. Close to Knight bridge but quiet!Very nice, clean and safe neighbourhood. Park just sits in front of the building. Location offers a quick walk to schools and transit!School catchment:Walter Moberly Elementary, David Thompson and Sir Winston Churchill Secondary. (28631692)

PublicRemarks: Centrally located next to Queen Elizabeth Park. Well designed by award-winning Cicozzi Architecture. This 2 bed 2 bath unit in the Contessa offers 9' ceilings, contemporary interiors that feature open-plan layouts, wide plank engineered hardwood flooring throughout main living area, expansive windows, gourmet kitchens with stone counters, stainless steel appliances. PublicRemarks: Discover luxury living in Coal Harbour! This 2-bed, 2-bath corner unit boasts a den, solarium, & stunning northwest exposure with city, mountain & ocean views. The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet & spa-like ensuite, while the second bedroom offers generous space. The kitchen is a chef's delight with an island, gas range & ample storage. Enjoy the cozy electric fireplace in the living room & host family dinners in the spacious dining area or BBQ on your private balcony while taking in the views. Perfectly located steps from the marina & seawall, you can walk downtown in minutes, with Vancouver's renowned restaurants at your fingertips. The well-maintained building offers resort amenities, including a rooftop pool, BBQ area, sauna/steam room, gym, & concierge. (29120887)

PublicRemarks: False Creek. This 2-bedroom plus den residence on the 26th floor offers awe-inspiring vistas of False Creek, the mountains, and the cityscape. PublicRemarks: Presenting One Pacific luxurious 2 bedroom + solarium + den, 2 bath floor plan! This spacious 983 sq ft. corner unit apartment features floor to ceiling windows facing False Creek Water Views. Upscale kitchen with Meile appliances, quartz counter tops, marble backsplash/flooring, wide plank engineered hardwood flooring, luxury hotel like washroom featured marble tile and under-mount sinks. California Closets throughout with a large walk-in in the master bedroom. One Pacific offers resort style amenities which includes large outdoor pool, hot tub, Lounge/Party room, 24 hour concierge & much more! PLUS rooftop deck and access to the amenities in the ARC as well. Includes 1 parking and 2 storage. Centrally located and steps from the seawall, shopping, lounges, restaurants, entertainment, Skytrain, Rogers arena, BC Place and much more! Pets and rentals allowed. Furniture included *turnkey* option available. Open house: Saturday, February 17 2:00pm to 4pm (29218512)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Promenade at the Quay by Polygon! This LUXURIOUS 2 Bed + 2 Bath condo with UNOBSTRUCTED WATER + SHIPYARD VIEWS is a MUST-SEE home! Features include an excellent floor plan with separated bedrooms, airy 9 ft ceilings, engineered hardwood flooring in the main living area & wool carpet in the bedrooms. Beautiful kitchen offers high-end Bosch appliances, 5-burner gas stove, a large fridge with ice maker, sleek quartz countertops & a stunning marble backsplash. Primary bedroom offers a spa-like en-suite bathroom with large walk-in shower, marble wall tiles, integrated bench seating & rain shower head. This home also includes a MASSIVE outdoor balcony space! Amenities: fitness studio, lounge with pool table & a large community patio. Steps to the Sea Bus, restaurants & shopping! 1 Parking + 1 Locker included. (29334029)

PublicRemarks: The Award winning Melville located in the heart of Coal Harbour radiates a commanding, majestic presence. Prestigious 2bdrms, 2 full baths plus 1 den with airy 9' ceilings, and H/W flooring, and cozy fire place. Master bedroom will accommodate a king size bed, complete with walk in closet, ensuite with deep soaker tub overlooking city and separate large shower stall. Perfect location for shopping, downtown, Stanley Park and Coal Harbour seawall. Full amenities such as beautiful rooftop sky garden with 40" lap outdoor pool and hot tub, fully equipped gym with water view! Comes with resident's lounge, children play outdoor area, games and media room with large TV on the terrace level, 24hr concierge, 1 parking and 1 storage included. (29240738)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to this well-maintained Coach House  just one block off the best part of The Drive. A Georgie Award Winner, and it's easy to see why with this thoughtful space comprising 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a mud room/den and an updated kitchen and bathrooms. The first floor opens to a mudroom /den/ laundry room. Up, you will find 2 bedrooms on the main, a large living room with a vaulted ceiling, and a cosy fireplace. There is a SW-facing patio and a perfect dining area off the recently renovated kitchen with s/s appliances and a gas range. An iron and wood staircase takes you upstairs to a huge principal bedroom with a full ensuite bathroom. An exterior storage room & lots of crawl space storage. Pets & rentals allowed. Easy to Show (29329647)

PublicRemarks: Stunning Southwest corner home with impressive park views & over 200sf of outdoor space in Eastpark by Boffo Properties. PublicRemarks: Foreshore Business Park is primely located in South Vancouver, one block off Marine Drive between Fraser Street and Main Street. This riverfront business park is situated to provide easy access to Downtown Vancouver, Vancouver International Airport and key transportation routes throughout Metro Vancouver. The main floor warehouse area features one (1) grade level front loading door, one (1) washroom, three phase 100 amp power, excellent lighting and 10' to 19' ft. clear ceiling heights in rear. The second floor office area features two (2) private offices, boardroom, excellent lighting system, kitchenette, one (1) washroom and T-bar ceiling. Three (3) parking stalls available including loading area. Please telephone or email listing agents for further information or to set up a showing. (34506071)

PublicRemarks: Waterfront location with 1,488 SF of living space. 2 Bedroom and huge Den/Office, totally renovated in 2022 including AC! East and South facing, town house like corner unit, Lonsdale Quay location next to Waterfront Park, Spirit Trail, Sea Bus. The adjacent building to the south (15 Chesterfield Place) owned by CNV is planned to be removed, extending Waterfront Park and creating a city/water view for this home. The location and size is a rare find, steps to everything, no car required! One parking, owner currently rents a second spot, lots of visitor parking, storage locker. (29235466)

PublicRemarks: Rarely available opportunity to purchase a AAA office space in a fantastic location in Downtown Vancouver in the iconic Burrard Place building. Burrard Place is a LEED Gold building with world-class amenities! Dedicated boardrooms , free wifi in all amenity areas, Meinhardt's grocery and cafe on main floor, commercial office shower and change rooms, 4 loading docks and elevators. You also get access to Club One amenities which include: first - class fitness facility, full-length lap pool, hot tub steam room, and sauna, private spa rooms, wine cellar and wine tasting bars, private dining facilities, outdoor dining and lounge, indoor and outdoor yoga space, and more. (34165239)

PublicRemarks: Why settle for a duplex or townhouse when you can own a detached 2 level charming home? This sun-drenched sanctuary, nestled west of Main St, boasts a fully-fenced yard on a 17.5x115.5 ft lot. Renovated with care, it features a new cedar fence, automatic power back gate, sleek tile flooring, updated bathrooms, and a kitchen with fresh cabinets and quartz countertops. Upstairs offers spacious living & dining areas, a modern kitchen, and a serene primary bedrm. Downstairs includes a second bedrm, full bathroom, mechanical room with ample storage, and a versatile den. Located near Marine Gateway for shopping and dining, with downtown just a 25-minute skytrain ride away. J.W. Sexsmith Elem and Churchill catchments. Ideal for a young family seeking long-term comfort and convenience. Must See! (29358910)

PublicRemarks: Beautiful rarely available 3 level, 3 bathroom, 4 bedroom, 9 year old townhouse including a suite. Views of the water, North Shore mountains, and some city. Fabulous 480 Sq. ft of top deck as well as a deck off the living room and Primary bedroom plus a rear patio off of the downstairs suite. Great floor plan with open concept kitchen with neutral colour scheme. Arguably one of the best neighbourhoods in East Vancouver. Plenty of parks, greenery and biking paths at your doorstep. Fabulous restaurants, breweries, shops and recreation within walking distance. Short drive or bike ride to downtown and the North Shore. Pets and rentals allowed, must see to appreciate. Showing by appointment only. (29078391)

PublicRemarks: Discover the epitome of urban luxury at The ARC. This exquisite 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom unit on the 20th floor offers an expansive 900 square feet of living space, complemented by breathtaking city, mountain, and water views. Convenient access to the the Sky Club, a unique feature of The ARC, grants access to a glass-bottom indoor pool on the 20th floor, a steam and sauna room, a chic coffee bar and lounge, a spacious party room, a 24-hour concierge, and a gym with stunning city and water views. Situated at the crossroads of convenience, this residence provides easy access to all that the city offers. Indulge in luxurious living at The ARC, where every detail is designed to elevate your lifestyle. (29304328)

PublicRemarks: Located at gateway to Lower Lonsdale, CentreView offers the ability to live, work, shop, play right at your doorstep. This 867 SQFT Corner unit, 2 beds, 2 full baths, open-concept living and modern finishings including integrated paneled appliances and flat-panel cabinetry.  Bedroom boasts a spacious walk-in closet and premium wide-plank flooring.  Enjoy access to CentreView's exclusive 25,000 sqft Wellness Centre, featuring a 3,300 sqft professionally-equipped gym, squash court, lounge, pool and hot tub.  Parking & storage included. Rentals and pets allowed. Enjoy fine dining, cafes, markets and shops, museum, galleries, and more!  All steps to your door with access to extensive biking and walking paths,  the SeaBus and Downtown Vancouver! Open house 2-4PM Saturday Feb 3 ,2024 (29213925)

PublicRemarks: Experience luxury urban living at Jameson House, designed by renowned architect Norman Foster, a 1,027 sq. ft. unit featuring 2 bedrooms & 2 baths. Situated with a northwest orientation, it offers captivating views of the mountains, city skyline, and glimpses of the water. PublicRemarks: Welcome to Primrose, discover the luxurious living with Queen Elizabeth Park as your backdrop in the heart of Vancouver's Westside. Unit 204 is a tranquil southeast corner unit comprising 2 bedRM+1 den+1 flex+2 bathRM+1 spacious 150 sqft patio with private walkout entrance. This unit features modern Italian Binova cabinetry, quartz countertops and backsplash, Grohe fixtures, frameless glass shower enclosures, Miele appliances, and 9ft ceilings. Prime location within easy walking distance of QE Park, 5-minute drive to VanDusen Garden and Oakridge Mall, and a 10-minute drive to UBC or Downtown Vancouver. Steps away from Skytrain, Eric Hamber High School, Children's Hospital, and Hillcrest and restaurants along the Cambie and Main street corridor. (28980801)

PublicRemarks: W63 Mansion is located in the prestigious Westside of Vancouver on W63rd Avenue; a quiet street lined with trees that come alive with cherry blossoms during the springtime. PublicRemarks: Welcome to The Triton just off Granville-a blend of city convenience and modern luxury. This 1243 sq. ft., 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom + solarium has been recently renovated with a new kitchen, bathrooms, flooring and all new appliances. Tons of custom cabinetry has been added. The ensuite has infloor heating and has been totally updated with new walk in shower and brand new vanity and dual sinks.  Located just a block from the new South Granville Skytrain. Indulge in nearby shopping, dining, cafes and theatres that enrich your urban living experience. The property includes parking and storage. Pet-friendly with rentals allowed (no short term).  Come by and have a look. (29264165)

PublicRemarks: Rare opportunity to own in the most prestigious AAA Office Tower in Vancouver; brand new Bosa Waterfront Centre. Across the Waterfront Skytrain and Seabus Station, steps to Coal Harbour and Gastown. Work from this new AAA world class building with all the best shops, hotels, and restaurants right outside your door. Perfect for any company who wants to impress. Building features A/C, Elegant Lobby with Concierge and sitting areas, 10 high-speed elevators, Common Lounge with full kitchen and breath-taking Ocean Views on the 28th floor featuring 2 common Boardrooms, Common Rooftop with indoor lounge, Fitness Facility, Bike / Commuter Facility with Showers and Lockers, Dinning areas, Yoga Studio, and much much more. There is no competition for this building. Units are in Semi-finished conditioned; Roller blinds included, pre finished ceiling frame, and individual electric panels. 6 common bathrooms on every floor. Very impressive! Can be combined with unit #550. Both also offered for lease. 1 Parking included (34255018)

PublicRemarks: Belpark is a magnificent Intracorp development set between the serene Winona Park & the prestigious Langara Golf Course. 2 bed, 2 full bath, & flex space are all included in this large, 1082 sq.ft. home. The kitchen is a culinary heaven, complete with premium Gaggenau appliances including a built-in wine cooler, imported Italian cabinets, gorgeous quartz countertops, & a stunning marble slab backsplash. Both bathrooms radiate elegance with heated marble floors, accent walls, & classic Dornbracht fixtures. The primary bed has a walk-in closet decorated with ambient lighting. Enjoy the luxury of A/C & a peaceful view of the green surroundings. Amenities include a game room, a gym, & a concierge. Close proximity to Downtown, Langara Golf Course, YVR, Marine Gateway, Oakridge & Public Transit. Includes 2 parking & 1 storage (29240040)

PublicRemarks: This beautifully renovated suite in the Beach District offers a bright and airy atmosphere, with two spacious bedrooms, den, and ample storage. PublicRemarks: Experience waterfront living at The Avila! Location, location, location! It doesn't get better than this. This west-facing 3-bed, 2-bath property boasts a functional floor plan that maximizes space. Nestled next to the Bayshore Hotel, it offers hardwood floors, recently renovated bathrooms & kitchen with a gas range, a spacious pantry, a cozy gas fireplace, & an expansive outdoor deck. The building provides top-notch amenities, including a 24-hr concierge, a ping pong room, a squash court, large indoor pool, & a conference/movie theatre room. Just steps away, you can access the seawall & Stanley Park within minutes! This offering includes 1 parking spot and 1 underground storage space. Don't miss out; call today to schedule your private viewing. ** SUNDAY FEB 18th 2-4PM ** (29302962)

PublicRemarks: Recently renovated townhouse in Langara Springs. This end unit boasts 1667 sqft of bright and spacious living space, featuring north, west, and east exposures. The well-designed floor plan includes generously sized rooms, sunken living room with a fireplace can be the 3rd bedroom, dining room, family room, and an updated kitchen on the main floor. Step outside to enjoy a garden patio with beautifully landscaped surroundings and direct access to the lagoon. A south-facing patio off the living room. PublicRemarks: Avison Young is pleased to present the opportunity to acquire a move-in ready small-bay industrial strata unit. The unit boasts a 1,183 sf warehouse, accompanied by 599 sf of mezzanine office space. The mezzanine layout features a common area, two private offices, a convenient kitchenette, and two bathrooms (one on the upper level and one full accessible bathroom on the lower level).   Conveniently nestled between Main Street and Fraser Street in South Vancouver's industrial market, the property is in proximity to SE Marine Drive, Oak Street and Knight Street, providing excellent access to multiple major trucking & arterial routes, as well as YVR airport. The area is also home to an abundance of retail and service amenities including Marine Gateway, 26 SW Marine Drive Commercial Development and the proposed Marine Gateway 2 mixed-use project. (34527263)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to your beautiful 4 bed/2 bath half duplex with a private front yard and mountain view in an amazing neighbourhood. The upper floor features a bright and spacious open floorplan with 9' ceilings, gourmet kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The living room has a cozy gas fireplace and a bay window with a picturesque mountain view. Engineered hardwood flooring, recessed lighting and radiant in-floor heating throughout the upper floor. The garden level has a potential for an in-law suite with its separate entrance. Beautifully landscaped private front yard and detached garage in the back. Amazing location-minutes to Commercial Dr, Skytrain, King Edward Village, schools and parks. Call today and see for yourself. (29169115)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to The Alvar, built by Concert Properties. This highly sought after Beach Avenue location is unbeatable with the seawall, Stanley Park and West End & Yaletown shopping just steps from your front door. This meticulously maintained unit has newer hardwood floors throughout, and an excellent 2 bedroom plus den floorplan with an open balcony. Features include air conditioning, floor to ceiling windows, an open kitchen that is great for entertaining, and a partial view of English Bay. ln the building enjoy a fitness centre, whirlpool/hot tub, media room,  games room and so much more! Two parking plus a large locker and lots of visitor parking. Suites in the building don't come for sale very often - don't miss this amazing opportunity. Easy to show! Open Sunday, Feb 25th from 2 to 4 pm. (29330499)

PublicRemarks: THIS IS IT. A RENOVATED NYC inspired loft that has it ALL. STYLE, SPACE & FUNCTION. Soaring 10'4 ceilings with huge timber beams/brick feature walls, a corner unit surrounded by 7' windows flooding in natural light/air and a nearly perfect 2 BR layout with huge office (could use as 3rd bedroom). Lovingly renovated, design cues and sophistication are evident at every angle. New kitchen/cabinets/appliances & beautiful dining area look over the expansive living room. The master suite is stunning, including a walk in closet, free standing claw-foot tub/shower and fireplace, Right in the heart of Gastown, live/work zoning steps from shopping/restaurants. Best private parking spot in the building too... (29236219)

PublicRemarks: Rare retail owner-occupier opportunity to purchase in the heart of Yaletown at Mainland Court. These units are completely upgraded and renovated featuring an open floor plan, large architectural glass windows, with an HVAC system. Currently built out as a lash studio, the space is versatile for a wide variety of retail and office uses. The units can be purchased vacant or as an investment with a leaseback option. The location is extremely well-situated for public transportation, just a 2-minute walk from the Yaletown Roundhouse Canada Line Skytrain Station and bus routes. The surrounding area encompasses Vancouver's trendiest retail, restaurants, and tech/creative office district, offering a perfect blend of work and leisure. (34515287)

PublicRemarks: A residential masterpiece- Wilshire house Shannon Wall Center Kerrisdale. This ultra-modern 2 bed 2 bath is well laid out with an open concept kitchen featuring high-end house-size stainless steel appliances, gas burners, and plenty of counter space to roll out your pie dough! The large master bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet, with 2 sinks luxurious ensuite bathroom. The whole complex is secluded behind heritage stone walls, mature trees and generous setbacks, elegant new residences and contemporary amenities intermingle with the heritage precincts. Thoughtfully connected via cobblestoned lanes, pathways and formal gardens with parks, ponds and unique places. 2 Parkings & 1 Locker. Welcome for showings. (29304683)

PublicRemarks: Step into pure luxury on the 28th floor of this trophy sub-penthouse, where breathtaking views await to captivate your senses. The expansive balcony, adorned with lush green turf, seamlessly merges indoor and outdoor living, offering unparalleled connection to the stunning mountain scenery. PublicRemarks: APERTURE living in the most desirable Westside area. The building is a Award-winning exterior design by architect Amo Matis! Inspired by iconic images of stacked timber and respond to the play of light. The floor-to-ceiling windows of each home are surrounded by frames- like apertures on a camera - that allow each home to receive maximum sun while minimizing glare. Enjoy the simple elegance of hardwood floors, wood veneer cabinetry and quartz countertops. Top of line Miele refrigerators, stoves and dishwashers blend seamlessly into the woodwork, creating an open, streamlined ambiance. This is faces South-West, with a large wrapped-around patio, perfect for summer entertainment. Gated-attached garage! Close to Oakridge Mall, Skytrain and everything! (29004662)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to a beautiful collection of homes that emphasizes community living. This 2 bedroom+lock-off home offers high ceilings, great kitchen & impressive amenities. It has a multigenerational layout with a separate unit that can used as an office, studio, or rental suite: additional income/mortgage helper. With its open-concept living & fully equipped suite, you'll have everything you need.This home also grants access to communal facilities, such as a courtyard, ample storage, laundry facilities, Modo car sharing & common house. The shared space features a full kitchen, lounge, & dining room, where residents can gather for group activities, communal meals, & even childcare with friendly neighbours.The Passivhaus design ensures fresh air & energy efficiency (up to 90% savings on heating/cooling).The large triple-pane windows create a quiet environment. Conveniently located near buses, bikeways, recreation, QE Park, Oakridge & Main/Fraser shops. Perfect home for community-minded individuals.OH: Sunday 25, 1-3pm (29281990)

PublicRemarks: Investment opportunity waiting for you at Espana II! This corner unit offers 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a flex room, all wrapped in an open and spacious layout with floor-to-ceiling windows that provide captivating views of the city and False Creek. Gourmet kitchen featuring ample cabinetry, a large kitchen island with a breakfast bar, and a wine fridge. Modern finishes like laminate floors throughout and spa-like bathrooms with a stand-alone soaker tub and large format tile surround add a touch of luxury to your daily life. AirBNB and short-term rentals are allowed. You'll also have access to superb amenities, a concierge, lap pool, sauna, fitness centre, lounge, and visitor parking. Rogers Arena, Gastown, Chinatown, BC Place-all just a stone's throw away. (28901071)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Firenze II, situated in the vibrant heart of Downtown Vancouver West. This exceptional building is mere steps away from an array of the city's most trendy attractions, including Rogers Arena, BC Place, premier shopping destinations, a lush park, a bustling casino, the picturesque False Creek Seawall, an array of delectable restaurants, and much more. Captivating views from this 28th-floor unit, which has undergone tasteful updates, including a custom kitchen. Originally a spacious 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom unit with a den, it has been thoughtfully converted into a generously sized 1-bedroom with a den. This alteration extends the kitchen and dining room area, offering versatility that can effortlessly be reverted to its original floor plan. AirBNB and short-term rentals are allowed. (28901086)

PublicRemarks: Bomber Brewing is now for sale! This popular craft brewery has been established since 2014. Located in Vancouver, this beer manufacturer also comes with an award winning Taco Truck for additional revenue. Bomberito, its renovated tap room has indoor/outdoor seating divided by a large garage door with excellent street exposure on Vancouver's bike path. In business for nearly ten years, and known for its award winning lineup that can be found in liquor stores across the Lower Mainline, Vancouver Island and Alberta. Bomber Brewing , with its large production capacity, has put its cider/wine and distilled license to use by manufacturing successful ciders and RTD expressions by way of house, licensed and contract brands. With room for growth, do not pass up this amazing opportunity. Vendor financing available for qualified buyers. Contact listing agent for details. (34520521)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to a beautiful collection of homes that prioritize community living. This 3-bed, 2-bath TH combines functionality & comfort w/modern amenities. The main lvl features an open floor plan w/a well-appointed kitchen. Downstairs, you'll find 3 beds, a full bath, & laundry. With its open-concept living area and fully equipped suite, you'll have everything you need. This home grants access to communal facilities, such as a serene courtyard, Modo car sharing and a common house. The shared space features a full kitchen, lounge, & dining room, where residents can gather for group activities, communal meals, & even childcare w/friendly neighbours. The Passivhaus design ensures fresh air & energy efficiency, allowing for up to 90% savings on heating & cooling. Additionally, the large triple-pane windows create a quiet environment. Conveniently located near buses, bikeways, recreation, Queen Elizabeth Park, Oakridge & Main/Fraser St. shopping, this is the perfect home for community-minded individuals. (29330817)

PublicRemarks: Panorama City & Mountain views in the highly sought after Fairview Slopes. This 1570 sqft townhome features a bright and open plan with new laminate floors upstairs,stainless steel appliances, glass tile backsplash, wood burning fireplace, custom window coverings and light fixtures, California closets, separate garage/workshop and a large crawl space. Recent rainscreening done to most of building including all around this unit. South facing deck from kitchen and large North facing deck with gorgeous views of the mountains, downtown and the water. Walking distance to Granville Island, the Seawall and Charleston Park. Pets allowed (2 dogs/cats). (28953561)

PublicRemarks: Brand new REAR duplex in the highly sought after Killarney area. This stunning 4 bed and 3.5 bath 1/2 duplex offers a perfect blend of modern elegance, the kitchen features quartz countertops, plenty of cabinetry, and S/S appliances, creating a stylish and functional space. Cozy up by the electric fireplace in the spacious living area, while AC keeps you comfortable year-round. Step into your private oasis in the backyard which includes a spacious patio, perfect for gatherings. Your peace of mind is ensured with security cameras and an alarm system. A single-car garage plus a ceiling storage rack. This home is conveniently located within walking distance to Sir Standford Fleming Elementary School & David Thompson Secondary, transit and parks. A plethora of shopping and dining options are available nearby as well. Open House Sat/Sun 2-4PM. (29190077)

PublicRemarks: Sitings is pleased to introduce Thesis, a unified neighborhood concept, coming to Vancouver's Oakridge neighborhood from Alabaster Homes. It consists of 12 ground floor retail units facing West 49th Ave directly across the street from Langara College, and 13 commercial units over two floors with private outdoor patios facing the lane. Thesis is just a 5 minute walk from Langara 49th Ave station, which leads to downtown Vancouver or YVR Airport in less than 15 minutes. Transit stops along West 49th Ave also connect the area to Metrotown and Burnaby to the east and UBC to the west. It's also a short walk from many desirable shops and services including YMCA, Langara Park, Langara Golf Course, the upcoming Oakridge Park, Time Out Market, and many others. Available Sizes: Street Front Retail Units: 547 SF - 1,322 SF Ground Floor Commercial Units: 922 SF - 1,610 SF Second Floor Commercial Units: 337 SF - 905 SF Contact listing agents for more details. (34137570)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to The Charles! A boutique collection of 16 brand new two and three bedroom townhouses by Medallion Homes, Hawthorne Development and Edge Construction. Built to Passive House standards maximizing energy-efficiency and comfort with timeless craftsman exteriors and thoughtfully  curated interiors by Design Living. This 3-Bed + Den + Flex home is idea for families, 3-bedroom and a den up, soaring 14-ft vaulted ceilings in the primary, and spa-like bathrooms. Gourmet kitchen and living space on the main with front and back patios for entertaining. Downstairs find a flex space and direct access to your EV-ready parking stall. All of this in vibrant Cedar Cottage on a quiet tree-lined street. Enjoy peace of mind with a 10-year New Home Warranty. (29356812)

PublicRemarks: LA FORTUNA at 788 West 8th Avenue is a Unique Development Opportunity. A 19 strata lot complex, located on the Southeast Corner of 8th & Willow Street, 1 block to Broadway. Situated in the "Uptown/Cambie North - Area A" of the Broadway Plan that supports building heights of up to 32 storeys for commercial developments (e.g. Medical Strata Office, Hotel, Strata/Rental Office etc). Comparable development applications propose FSR of 6-8. The plan strives to create key office locations and health districts in the heart of Vancouver, and facilitate a "Second Downtown". Contact the listing agent for more information and details on this HOT potential development opportunity. (29085357)

PublicRemarks: Rarely available and unique live/work loft in the sought after Hudson on Granville Street in the heart of Downtown Vancouver! PublicRemarks: Welcome to HARLIN, a collection of 334 homes in River District. Located just steps away from all the restaurants, shops, and services in River District Town Centre and a 1.5km waterfront path, life at Harlin is just as easy as it is exciting. Enjoy stunning sunsets from this elegant West facing 1 bed home on the 18th floor with modern design & comfort. This home offers refined living experience w/luxury finishes and high end Fulgor Milano kitch appliances. Well-designed, timeless interiors w/8'10" ceilings. Luxurious amenities located on the 29th and 30th floor incl. 2 barrel saunas, hot tub, coworking spaces with 2 privacy pods, fitness centre, guest suite, mini golf & much more. Limited time offer,3% credit & deposit incentive* *Subject to terms and conditions. Contact us for more details. (29307232)

PublicRemarks: FORUM by CHARD Development offers a unique opportunity to acquire retail, light industrial, or office spaces in the thriving Marine Gateway neighborhood of South Vancouver. PublicRemarks: Welcome to SIENNA COURT, a boutique townhouse community by highly regarded Alaris Developments. Located in centrally located and sought after Cedar Cottage with excellent schools, a wide variety of shops, great cafes and incredible restaurants all just minutes from your front door. This well-appointed end-unit has 2 bedrooms and a large den/3rd bedroom, 2 bathrooms and a full size private attached garage. Highlighted by the stunning kitchen with two tone cabinetry, gas range, island with bar seating, quartz counters and backsplash, microwave drawer and access to the balcony for your bbq. Radiant in-floor heat, HW on-demand, hardwood flooring throughout, ample storage, great curb appeal, low strata fees, beautiful finishing details. OPEN HOUSE Sat Feb 17 & Sun Feb 18 2-4pm. (29294469)

PublicRemarks: Turner's Dairy pioneers 1 3 unique townhouses on 2 single-family lots, while being a love letter to its historic form. The new development offers two and three-storey residences designed for contemporary and efficient living suited for the modern family. Picture clean lines, top of the line appliances, ample storage, and a home that lets you dictate how you live in it. AIRstudio sought out to create homes that embodied environmental, social and economic pillars which are essential to the future of the neighbourhood and the city. In this unparalleled location in the heart of Mount Pleasant, these homes will answer your needs for active families, foodies, and those seeking cool modern architecture. 1 Parking and 1 Storage included with all units. OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY FEB 18TH 2-4PM. (29281968)

PublicRemarks: Open Saturday February 17th 2-4pm  Open Sunday February 18th 2-4pm  Welcome you to your Brand New Residence. 3 Level Front Unit 1/2 Duplex by Long Term Builder. No Strata Fees. Move in Ready. 1,391 sq ft., 9ft Ceilings. 3 Bedrooms. 3 and Half Bathrooms. Beautiful Bright and Open Concept, 3 ft wide Gas Stove. Big Island for Entertaining. Electric Fireplace. Garage and 1 Open Parking. Front Yard. Quiet Residential Street. School Catchment: K - 7 Dr. A.R. Lord Elementary and 8 - 12 Templeton Secondary. Close to Boundary Road. Easy Access to Hwy 1 and Lougheed Hwy and Hastings. Short Distance to North Shore, Downtown Vancouver. Unit 2 (back unit also for sale)2-5-10 Year Home Warranty. (29364993)

PublicRemarks: Introducing  Asanti homes newest 1/2 duplex in the desirable Renfrew neighbourhood known for being quiet and family-friendly, making it a great place to raise a family. This spacious 1441sq. ft. North facing home offers 3 bedrooms 3.5 bathrooms with 2 ensuite bathrooms. Notable features include heat pump forced air heating/cooling for year-around comfort, integrated fisher and paykel appliances, custom storage cabinetry, quartz countertops, Gas Fireplace, built in Kitchen bench w/storage and hardwood flooring. The construction quality and finishing are unparalleled. This North facing home is conveniently located with easy access to downtown Vancouver and Highway 1, shopping and AR Lord Elementary/Our Lady of Sorrows/Templeton Secondary/Notre Dame Secondary. PublicRemarks: The subject property comprises a total of 2,120 sqft of warehouse/office space. The ground floor features 1,060 sqft of warehouse/showroom space, a reception area, a front-grade level loading door, and a handicap-accessible washroom. The second floor consists of 1,060sqft. of fully built-out office space with open area, a large boardroom, two rooms, and a kitchenette. Located in South Vancouver's industrial hub, the property is a short drive from Knight Street and Marine Drive corridors, providing direct routes to downtown Vancouver and Richmond. Proximity to the Canada Line's Marine Drive Station enhances public transport accessibility. The area is vibrant with diverse businesses, fostering networking opportunities. Adjacent to the Fraser River, it provides a scenic backdrop and leisure spots for breaks and after-work activities. (34538578)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Marco Polo by Gryphon, a mixed-use commercial building coming to Oakridge District. Strategically located at Cambie and W49th Ave, Marco Polo sits at the crest of the Cambie Corridor. Not only is it adjacent to the Langara-49th Ave SkyTrain station, but also the future R4 RapidBus connecting UBC to Metrotown. 13 retail units, 198 AAA strata office units, 45 residential units coming next year, and 360 parking stalls, Marco Polo is the new way to live and work in balance. Beyond the office, Strata members can enjoy complimentary access to The Curator Club, a private club within the building spanning 10,000 square feet. The exclusive amenities include a range of workplace and wellness features, such as co-working lounges, a double-height multi-functional atrium, meeting rooms, and a 4,000 sqft fitness centre. (34585323)

PublicRemarks: TRES LUXE, TRES CHIC, L'Hermitage, an elegant boutique 5 star luxury residence in the heart of Downtown Vancouver! Meticulously maintained and Grand Lobby entrance. Coveted Original Developer Show home Display Suite. This 1374 sqft Sky Home Condo features Vancouver's most beautiful Panoramic Skyline Views from the North Shore Mountains to English Bay. 2 Bedroom & den (can be a 3rd Bedroom) 2 spa bathrooms, 9-ft ceilings, 2 balconies & 2 Parking. This Air Conditioned open plan Dream Home features a Millenium open kitchen with large centre island, Stainless Steel Bosch Appliances & Lg Hood Fan, SubZero fridge, Eggersman German Cabinetry, gas cooktop, limestone counter tops. Two spa inspired marble bathrooms with a deluxe soaker tub. In suite storage. Custom millwork throughout, gorgeous wood paneling, California closets, Automated Lutron Roller Shades, Smart Home System Custom drapery & Bocci lighting. 24 hr Elite Concierge services. Pets & Rentals Allowed. (29362095)

PublicRemarks: Waterfront living at Azura! Spectacular view home with 2 bedroom, 2 full bath + office in Yaletown. Enjoy beautiful SW protected views of False Creek and park. This 1124 sqft bright spacious open plan offers ample room for you to relax and entertain. Enjoy your morning coffee or BBQ on your private balcony and take in the views. This desirable SW exposed home provides the ultimate in privacy and convenience... all in one of Yaletown's premier bldgs. Club Viva offers 20,000 sqft of amenities with a huge fitness room, pool, hot tub, squash courts, billiards lounge and movie theatre! This special home comes with 2 sxs parking and 1 storage locker. BBQ's OK. Pets OK 2 dogs or 2 cats. Rentals min 30 days. A/C can be also be installed! Tenanted. Showings require min 24 hrs notice, by appt only. (29330877)

PublicRemarks: PENTHOUSE AT MUSEE! In one of the most sought after central, chic, and stylish locations of the Vancouver West Side, South Granville. You will fall in love with this bright spacious 1,042 Sq. Ft. 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with over 500 Sq. Ft. private roof top deck is perfect for all your needs! This rarely available home features high-end appliances such as Bosch & Fisher Paykel, stunning granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, hardwood flooring, in-suite storage, and bright office space and a modern electric fireplace. Amenities include a meeting room, state-of-the-art fitness centre, and child play area. Central to Broadway & Burrard corridor making it a quick walk to Granville Island, Granville Street shops, cafes , restaurants such as Tap & Barrel Bridges, Earls, Cactus Club, and much much more! Live mere steps to Downtown Vancouver with all the convenience and none of the noise. 2 Parking stalls included. DonÂ´t miss this opportunity! (29266899)

PublicRemarks: Own a piece of iconic architecture in South Oak. Designed by award-winning Arno Matis, Oku is zero emissions concrete construction offering 132 homes in 3 boutique buildings. The superior window and wall structure is designed for energy efficiency and reduced sound transmission. All-season comfort from best-in-class VRF air-conditioning technology. Each home features luxurious interiors with a sleek gourmet kitchen equipped with quartz countertops and European stainless steel appliances. Building amenities include a fitness studio, co-working space, entertainment lounge for group gatherings. Conveniently located in a well-established Vancouver West neighbourhood with easy access to Churchill Secondary, Sir Wilfred Laurier Elementary, Oakridge Centre, YVR and downtown. www.okuliving.com. (28954326)

PublicRemarks: Rarely available and highly thought after 04 plan in Cambie Gardens! Engineered HW flooring & carpet in bedrooms, heating & cooling system, & automated lighting with sleek roller shades. PublicRemarks: This charming craftsman bungalow is tucked amongst a handful of character homes on one of Renfrew's prettiest streets. Home has upgraded plumbing and 100A electrical service -- including installation of heat pumps for multi-zone air conditioning. Newer roof, front/back exterior porch & stairs, re-insulated attic provide a solid base for future renos. Gleaming hardwood fir floors lie hidden underneath existing flooring. Enjoy views of the North Shore Mountains from the rear of this home, situated on a flat lot with lane access. High ceiling height in basement allows for potential expansion. Conveniently walk to the shops of Commercial Drive/Hastings Street, Clinton Park, and plaza mall at 1st/Renfrew, with a Walk Score of 87! (29329687)

PublicRemarks: Charming coach house located in the heart of Kitsilano. With 2 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this property offers a comfortable & modern living space. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors, high-end finishes, and an abundance of natural light throughout. The tall vaulted ceilings create an airy atmosphere, while the gas fireplace adds warmth and coziness. The open-concept layout is perfect for entertaining, and the french doors provide easy access to the front patio. Kitchen features stone countertops, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash, w/gas cooktop & hood fan. The spa-inspired bathroom adds a touch of luxury, and the private back patio w/gas hookup is ideal for relaxation or outdoor dining. Do not miss on this stunning Kitsilano coach house! (29327922)

PublicRemarks: This location perfectly blends all the benefits of a 3 BR family home with all of the action in the Lower Lonsdale and famous Ship YardÂ District. Skip the house maintenance and chores and spend more quality familyÂ time with less commuting.Â  Enjoy the ocean, skyline and sunset views from the comfort of your SW air conditioned corner suite. Your indoor plants and balcony gardens will thrive with floor-to-ceiling windows that allow natural light to pour in all day. PublicRemarks: Welcome to 35 Park West on the Cambie Corridor. Built in 2019, this 3 bedrooms plus den and 2 bathrooms 1236 sq. ft with air conditioning. 2 cars garage(one is EV ready) and a locker for storage. Located at the heart of Vancouver with only minutes away from restaurants such as Landmark Hotpot, King Edward or Oakridge Skytrain stations, the new Oakridge Center in the near future and Queen Elizabeth Park! PublicRemarks: Introducing a symmetrical upper and lower 2480 square foot duplex in the heart of Cedar Cottage and just steps from Clark Park. PublicRemarks: Discover a charming historical hair salon shop in North Vancouver's most prime location.With timeless elegance interior design, it caters to discerning clientele. The property's rich heritage and captivating facade draw in foot traffic, leaving a lasting impression. Its generous floor space accommodates stylish hair stations, luxurious wash basins, and cozy waiting areas. Strategically located on a bustling street, it enjoys high visibility and footfall, making it a coveted spot for locals and tourists alike. The business itself is thriving with a loyal customer base and skilled remarkable chance to own both a prime property and a flourishing stylists. Don't miss this business. (33981273)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to this South-West facing 3 Bedroom unit at PARK HOUSE SOUTH, an iconic concrete park side building designed by award-winning FRANCL Architecture. Bordered by Winona Park & Langara Golf Course. Steps from urban convenience of growing South Cambie Hub and future skytrain station. A well laid out unit that focus not only functionality but also privacy driven. Gourmet kitchen by Italian Scavolini, equipped with Miele appliance package and Caesarstone countertops with waterfall edge on the expansive kitchen island. Spa-like baths with floor to wall tiles throughout, Grohe fixtures, built-in medicine cabinets. Air-conditioning and 9 feet ceiling for extra comfort inside. Two parking stalls including one EV Stall fulfills your needs in the coming future. Open House Sat. Feb.10, 2-4pm (29282275)

PublicRemarks: BRAND NEW STRATA 1/2 DUPLEX, Front Duplex. Built by Experience Builder PD Moore Homes, an award-winning builder in East Vancouver. Luxury meets contemporary style. Back Unit also available for sale. Both units have 3 bdrms plus a den/office. 2.5 bathrooms. Heat Pump. HRV. The interior finishes are clean, modern, and solid. Integrated Security System. Each unit has a 1-car garage which has been fitted to store tools/bikes/seasonable items. These modern inspired homes have been crafted to ensure every tasteful touch and thoughtful feature will continue to delight for generations - redefining the Vancouver duplex market. 2-5-10 Year Home Warranty. Close to Parker Street and Renfrew Street and Notre Dame Secondary. Super Central! (29355667)

PublicRemarks: "The Melville" by AMACON. N/NW corner w/fantastic view of Coal Harbour, Marina, City, Mountain & Stanley Park.  Spacious Living & dining room + 2 bdrm + 2 bath + 2 office.  Offers S/S Appliances (Side-by-side Fridge, Gas Cook-top, DW, Built-in Oven & Microwave), Granite countertops, hardwood floors & outdoor balcony.  Amenities include:  Rooftop outdoor Pool, Hot Tub, BBQ Patio & Sky Garden, Gym and Sauna; 3rd floor lounge: Grand entertainment room + kitchen/wet bar, billiard table, library, meeting room and Kids Playground. Moreover, visitor parking and 24/7 Concierge.  Short walk to Harbour Green Park, Harbour Community Centre, United States Consulate, Vancouver Convention and Exhibition Centre, Canada Place, Seawall, Stanley Park, Transit, cafes, shops & Restaurants. Ready to move-in. (28959924)

PublicRemarks: High quality craftsmanship 3 level front half duplex! Presenting 1 - 2846 McGill Street, a newly built, modern 1/2 Duplex in Vancouver. Including 3 bedrooms all with private ensuites, powder room on the main floor, office nook and plenty of storage areas throughout. Features include air conditioning, HRV fresh air system, engine hardwood flooring, high quality stainless steel appliances, sensor LED lighting in all bathrooms, waterfall island, automatic roller blinds, 4 camera security system, full size LG washer and dryer, in-floor radiant heating and drop ceilings with pot lights through out the entire home. One covered parking space and a fully landscaped front entrance, gives the most ideal "at home" feeling. This one is a MUST SEE! Priced to sell! OPEN HOUSE FEB. 18TH 1-3PM. (29284893)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Telus Gardens-an iconic building in the heart of Downtown Vancouver! This RARELY AVAILABLE 3 Bed + Storage/Den + 2 Bath corner suite offers BEAUTIFUL PANORAMIC CITY VIEWS from almost every room! Bright and spacious floor plan with a large balcony spanning the width of the home. Highlights include integrated Miele appliances, gas cooktop, high-gloss cabinets, quartz countertops, convenient kitchen island with breakfast bar, sleek bamboo wood flooring & A/C! Steps to Vancouver's best restaurants, shopping, entertainment, parks & so much more! 1 parking stall included. OPEN HOUSE: SAT & SUN Jan 27th & 28th 2-4PM. (29193603)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Hanna - discover urban living at its finest in this 3-bed, 2-bath townhome perfectly situated between Fraser and Main Street. Quiet and tucked in the back of the complex with extra large windows throughout the home to bring in natural light, updated with Hunter-Douglas blinds. Modern luxury meets convenience with hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, and a private backyard. The open layout seamlessly connects living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for relaxation or entertaining. The extra large primary bedroom boasts an ensuite and multiple closets. Enjoy the private fenced backyard and direct access to the parkade with EV parking available. Open House: Sat, Feb 17 & Sun, Feb 18 from 2-4 PM. (29329613)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Cambie Star! This luxurious concrete LEED Gold project in the heart of the Cambie corridor offers a prime location and stunning features. This spacious 3-bed, 3 full bath suite boasts a south-west exposure, providing ample natural light. Situated on top of the Canada Line's King Edward station, this home offers easy access to transportation. Enjoy a short stroll to parks, including the beautiful QE Park, as well as various restaurants, shopping destinations, and amenities along the Cambie corridor. The suite itself impresses with a large open main living area, air conditioning, granite countertops, and engineered hardwood floors. Additional highlights include a covered patio and a gas stove. Includes 1 parking space and 1 storage unit. OPEN HOUSE SAT FEB 17 2 - 4PM. (29327925)

PublicRemarks: Home 3004 in the stylish Denna Collection at Apex, features 1374 square feet of living space. With a large, 168 square foot sun-filled terrace, a great floor plan with thoughtful design, custom Italian kitchen from INFORM and CHIL Interior Designs and equipped with high end appliances. 3 bedroom 3 bathroom home with stunning views of Burrard Inlet, North Shore, Burnaby & Vancouver. Parking for 2 vehicles, storage locker, HVAC on demand, balcony gas connections and more. Deanna Club is 14,000 SF facility which includes a 25-metre indoor lap pool, hot tub, steam room, dry sauna, fitness room, two multipurpose rooms & a spacious party room that residents can book for large gatherings. Call and book an appointment today. (29173018)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to 1603 E 4th Ave!! Stunning 3 BED + 2 BATH, Features open layout concept with a very functional 3 level floor plan with tons of natural light, Serene main living area with over 9ft ceilings & expansive windows with great flow. Upstairs features a large primary bedroom with en-suite, office space & HUGE balcony. If you want to generate income and don't need the other 2 bedrooms in the basement they can be converted to a lock off suite. PublicRemarks: This amazing house is located on a beautiful tree-lined street in Renfrew Heights, was taken down to studs in 2011 & rebuilt. Excellent condition with a functional layout, new roof, built-in vacuum, high-efficiency gas, hot water on demand & enviro paving in the backyard. Good value for growing family, walking distance to shopping, schools & parks. Don't miss it! OPEN HOUSE ON SAT & SUN (FEB 17-18)2-4PM (29349788)

PublicRemarks: 320 Granville Street, a recently completed, prestigious AAA Waterfront office building. It occupies a prime location, perfect for businesses seeking to cater to a discerning clientele. This location is particularly ideal for entrepreneurs desiring a premium office space enriched with unparalleled amenities for both employees and clients. Centrally positioned, it's a jewel in downtown Vancouver, tailor-made for tech firms, medical practices, and professional services that value face-to-face client interactions. The building's allure lies in its combination of prestige, state-of-the-art facilities, and access to a wealthy client base drawn to this urban sector. Proximity to the financial and business districts further underscores its strategic significance for professionals requiring an exclusive, high-caliber setting. Additionally, its convenient access to the Waterfront SkyTrain Station and the Seabus extends its reach, making it an exemplary choice for serving the diverse clienteles of Greater Vancouver. (34437362)

PublicRemarks: Experience executive living, just steps away from Alberni & Robson Street. This exquisite condo offers over 1000 SF of luxurious living space with a rare 400 SF wrap around patio. The double-door entrance invites you into the main area with large windows fitted with custom blinds showcasing city views, while flooding the space with an abundance of natural light. The open living room & kitchen concept features a large island, creating an ideal space for entertaining. Fully renovated in 2018, with built-in closets with sensor lights, a gas fireplace, and spacious bedrooms. 2 side by side parking stalls & 1 storage locker. Pets are allowed, no rental restrictions! Right by the vibrant shopping areas, seawall, and the bustling marina. (29262605)

PublicRemarks: PATINA BY RENOWNED DEVELOPER CONCERT PROPERTIES! 42 STOREY LUXURY LANDMARK BUILDING IN THE HEART OF DOWNTOWN VANCOUVER! High floor corner 2 bedroom plus solarium /den spacious suite with panoramic view of city skyline, mountains & ocean! Modern kitchen featuring quality granite counter tops & large island, high-end MIELE appliances including ceramic glass cooktop, dishwasher, built-in wall oven, hood fan & LIEBHERR B/1 fridge. 2 luxury bathrooms with a deep soaking tub, glass tile surround, frameless glass shower stall, double sinks, marble tops & heated floor in the master ensuite & a 2nd 3 pc bathroom w/frameless glass shower stall. PATINA features an excellent Concierge service, clubhouse, guest meeting room, exercise centre, a large rooftop garden and 3 elevators. (29129449)

PublicRemarks: Welcome home! This impressive 3BED/3BATH Scandinavian style home offers an unparalleled level of comfort and design.. As you step inside, you are greeted with an open concept layout and a stunning kitchen featuring a unique quartz backsplash and countertops, a luxurious Italian range hood by Faber is complemented with high end stainless steel appliances. The main floor also has a spacious bedroom and bathroom. The upper level consists of 2 sizable bedrooms, both equipped with their own ensuites, and a large rooftop deck with ample space for entertaining. Fully equipped with AC and radiant heating. Located in the heart of Vancouver, with shops and schools just a short distance away, you do not want to miss out on this! (29160934)

PublicRemarks: Popular #01 plan in the prestigious "THE MELVILLE" at Coal Harbour.  A bright 2 bedroom+Office+2 bathroom condo with a functional layout and beautiful water/city views. The building has amazing amenities including breath taking 360 degree views from the roof top deck on the 42nd level, pool, hot tub, gym, sauna and concierge. Perfect opportunity to own a new home or investment in prestigious Coal Harbour. Unit comes with 1 parking stall and 1 storage unit. Walking distance to Pacific Centre Shopping Mall, skytrain, Harbour Green Park, Coal Harbour Marina, Stanley Park and all world-class restaurants. (29335492)

PublicRemarks: Nestled on a quiet, residential street in the heart of Mount Pleasant, E15 is an extension of the neighbourhoodÃs vibrant energy. PublicRemarks: Garden Park brings a community of 5 residences to historic East Vancouver at 3rd & Templeton. This gorgeous back 1/2 duplex is part of the original revitalized heritage home & overlooks your private back patio. Modern elements fuse with a mindful preservation of East Van's charm. Open main floor with modern farmhouse style kitchen, spacious living room, & eating area. 2 attentively designed bdrms upstairs & 1 expansive bdrm on the lower level provide space for the whole family. This home comes fully equipped with A/C, in-floor radiant heat, security system & a detatched single car garage with EV outlet. Proudly built by Four Corners & Modern Style Homes, East Van's most reputable builders. www.gardenparkvancouver.ca (29334716)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to this beautiful back 1/2 duplex in Killarney! This elegant home features 3 bed/4 bath, private backyard, 1 car garage, & crawl space. A beautiful transitional interior with spacious living space and tons of natural light.. The upper level offers spacious bedrooms to live comfortably all with ensuites! The backyard gives a desirable outdoor space, perfect for growing families. The kitchen features high end Fisher Paykel Appliances with luxury quartz countertops. Radiant Heating, A/C, HRV, security, & EV charger allow you to stay comfy all seasons. Easy access to Skytrain, Metrotown, Central Park, shopping, etc . Open house or schedule viewing. Offers Mon Feb 19, 2024 by 4:00PM (29362671)

PublicRemarks: Another beautiful home built by 88 Homes Ltd. Contemporary, modern & sophisticated. Front to back 1/2 duplex in the heart of East Vancouver steps to Victoria Drive and Kingsway Street and all the shops you love. Open floor plan with quality craftsmanship and finishing's thru-out. Modern exterior with Hardy and Glass and low maintenance yard. Modern & functional interior features engineered floors, tiled baths, modern kitchens with Bosch appliances, AC, Radiant heat,  top floor bed has balcony with amazing panoramic city & mountain view. Cozy yet spacious, you'll love to entertain with the whole main wide open. Front unit has the entire front yard, rear unit has the back and a single garage for each. These homes are ultra cool, you'll love them. All this backed by a 2-5-10 New Home Warranty. (29240131)

PublicRemarks: *PRE-SALE OPPORTUNITY* - Welcome to 2776 McGill St!! PublicRemarks: One of the Vancouver's most prestigious waterfront buildings : Rogers Tower. Sought-after one bedroom luxury suite with spa-like ensuite. Spacious and open kitchen with eating bar, stunning granite countertops, huge double sink, Sub-Zero fridge, and stainless steel appliances by Fisher & Paykel. Breathtaking views of beautiful downtown Vancouver, harbour and North Shore Mountains. Steps away from exquisite shops and restaurants. Stroll or cycle to Stanley Park Seawall. Amenities include secure bike room, large gym, meeting rm, sauna,visitor parking and concierge services. Also included is one parking stall and one storage locker. (29369432)

PublicRemarks: TOWNHOME living in the heart of Downtown Vancouver at the landmark THE PACIFIC BY GROSVENOR, where quality meets a timeless design. Enjoy convenience of your front door to within steps of Seawall, Stanley Park, popular restaurants, parks and more. Interiors include meticulously planned 2-LEVEL, 2 BEDROOMS & 2 BATHS + FLEX, and high living room ceilings. Italian millwork by Snaidero is custom-configured for every kitchen, outfitted with professional-grade appliances from Sub-Zero, Wolf and Miele. Enjoy the interaction of Hornby Street featuring a 145 sq.ft. Patio with natural gas bib for BBQ. 2nd floor access to Lounge, & landscaped & outdoor terrace provides an area for cooking & dining. Amenities feature 24-hour Concierge, Fitness Centre, Games Room. Includes 1 parking & 1 storage locker. (29195876)

PublicRemarks: LEED Gold AAA brand new Office space located in the prestigious One Burrard Place near the corner of Hornby Street and Davie Street in the heart of downtown Vancouver. The building features include use of boardrooms, fitness facility, private spa and pool, outdoor dining and lounge areas, showers, change rooms and wine room. This fully air-conditioned 1,037 sq. ft. unit features lots of windows for an abundance of natural light, approved plans and specifications in place for high quality flooring, two (2) private offices and a coffee bar and sink. The unit has one (1) parking stall plus access to common area stalls. Please telephone or email listing agents for further information or to set up a viewing. (33791403)

PublicRemarks: Prime opportunity for an owner/user or an investor to purchase a strata retail unit located on the northeast corner of Davie and Richards Streets in Vancouver's trendy Yaletown neighbourhood. The Property consists of one legal strata lot totaling approximately 577 sq. ft. of area. The Property offers excellent frontage and prominent exposure onto Davie and Richards Streets. Yaletown is a bustling neighbourhood comprised of the city's top restaurants, cafes, unique retailers, and a tech/creative office district. Located just two blocks from the Yaletown Roundhouse Canada Line Station, the Canada Line provides direct connectivity from the Property to the Downtown Core, Waterfront Station, the Olympic Village, Vancouver International Airport, and Richmond. (34547828)

PublicRemarks: Gorgeous 3 bdrm + 3 full bath CONCRETE townhouse in W1 by renowned developer Concord Pacific. Main floor has approx 12'6ft high ceilings and owner has added an extra 90 sf loft that could be removed. Featured with central A/C, open living area, quality finishing with Miele appliances, gas cooktop, quartz countertop; Bathroom with marble tiles. Great amenities includes a professionally equipped fitness centre, 24 hours concierge, media room, karaoke room & an automatic touchless carwash facility. Unbeatable central location, steps from Canada Line/Bus loop, Cineplex theatre, banks, restaurants, Winners, Starbucks, Shoppers and T&T Supermarket. Minutes to Richmond, YVR Airport and DT, Churchill Secondary. 2 side by side EV parking stalls and 1 Locker included. Open House Sat Nov 25th 1-3pm. (29036541)

PublicRemarks: Located in Renfrew just steps from schools, shopping, and restaurants, this elegant board and batten finished home features 4 bed/4 bath with stunning views of the North Shore mountains. The main floor includes a well thought out layout maximizing living space. The kitchen boasts built in Fisher Paykel appliances, slide out microwave, and a large island. 3 bed/2 bath upstairs of which 2 bedrooms have unobstructed North Shore views. The basement offers extra space which can be used as a multi purpose room or converted into a studio suite. Additional features include engineer hardwood flooring, Radiant Floor Heat, A/C, HRV, security, EV charger, 2/5/10 Warranty, and crawl space for storage.  Open house Feb 10 2-4PM and then offers Monday Feb 12 at 4PM (29323628)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the esteemed 1888 Alberni Residences. This luxurious 2 bdr, 2 bth condo blends classic elegance & modern flair in Vancouver's West End. At 1,483sqft, it offers stunning views of the North Shore Mtns and Coal Harbour, close to Stanley Park and Denman & Robson. The interior open-plan living space elegantly combines the living, dining, and family areas, making it an entertainer's dream. The master suite is a tranquil retreat with a marble ensuite, underfloor heating, and ample closet space, while the 2nd bdr is perfect as a guest room or office. With $50K+ in upgrades, this condo defines luxury. Amenities include an indoor pool, sauna, hot tub, and gym in this exclusive 36 suite community. 1prk and a large lkr, Pets OK. Open Feb 17/18. Strata Doc Report: http://tinyurl.com/yc2rytke (29354943)

PublicRemarks: A MUST SEE! No expense spared int he quality and craftsmanship in the back half of this duplex. Introducing 2-2846 McGill Street, a newly built, modern 1/2 duplex in Vancouver. This 3 level home provides plenty of space. Features include air conditioning, HRV fresh air system, engineered hardwood flooring, high quality stainless steel appliances, full size LG washer and dryer. Sensor LED lighting in all bathrooms, automatic roller blinds, waterfall counter top, 4 cameral security system, in-floor radiant heating and drop ceilings with pot lights throughout the entire home. PublicRemarks: Welcome to SIENNA COURT, a boutique townhouse community by highly regarded Alaris Developments. Marie Design-Natural Oak hardwood flooring, Caeserstone kitchen countertops & backsplash, Miele appliances, Blomberg washer & dryer, contemporary walk-through shower with quartz linear drain, large niche & Hansgrohe brushed nickel shower outlet. Secure gated underground parking (2 parking inc). 2-5-10 year warranty. https://linaliving.com/ (29009815)
